\s1 K…ôbeŇčn…õ k…ôp…ĒŇč 
\p  
\v 42 K…Ē Yesu embeŇčn…õ Ňča nt…õ: ¬ęMba k…Ē fum …Ēs…ĒŇč…õ wanf…õt w…ôkin k…ôloŇč…õ awut akaŇč…õ dac…Ē nw…õ …õŇčgb…õk…ôr im k…ôlaŇč k…Ēn m…Ē-…õ, kiti ka w…ôkayi k…ôyeŇčk k…ôtas t…Ēk…Ē aŇčkot…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē tasar p…Ēp…ĒŇč d…ôkilim pal…ôm k…Ē d…ôk…ôba m…Ē.  
\v 43 K…Ē k…ôca kam k…ôndes…ĒŇč'am k…ôciya-…õ, m…ôgbinti ki! Bawo k…ôb…õr…õ kiyi kam ka doru o doru m…ôy…Ē k…ôca kin k…ôncep…ôr k…ôl…ôm kam yahanama d…ôn…õnc nd…õ d…Ēnt…Ēnim…õ m…Ē, m…ôy…Ē waca m…õr…ôŇč.  
\v 44 \f + \fr 9:44 \ft Yecic…ôs y…Ēgb…Ēk…ôr…õ y…Ēl…Ēma yendeŇč…ôr: ¬ęYahanama, y…õt ny…õ y…ĒŇčs…Ēm dis m…Ē y…Ēf…Ēfi, n…õnc nd…õ d…Ēnc…Ēf dis m…Ē d…Ēf…Ēnim…õ.¬Ľ\f* 
\v 45 K…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ k…ôc…ôk kam k…ôŇčs…ĒŇč'am k…ôciya-…õ, m…ôgbinti ki. K…ôb…õr…õ kiyi kam ka doru o doru m…ôy…Ē k…ôc…ôk kin k…ôncep…ôr k…ôl…ôm kam yahanama m…ôy…Ē w…õc…ôk m…õr…ôŇč.  
\v 46 \f + \fr 9:46 \ft Yecic…ôs yokur y…Ēl…Ēma yendeŇč…ôr: ¬ęD…ôndo y…õt ny…õ y…Ēs…Ēm dis y…Ēf…Ēfi, d…ôndo n…õnc d…Ēf…Ēnim…õ haŇč dabada.¬Ľ\f* 
\v 47 K…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ d…Ēf…Ēr dam d…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč'am k…ôciya-…õ, m…ôkakti di. K…ôb…õr…õ kam akip Ňča d…õb…õ da Kanu d…ônt…Ēf m…ôy…Ē d…Ēf…Ēr din k…ôncep…ôr k…ôl…ôm kam yahanama m…ôy…Ē f…Ēr m…õr…ôŇč.  
\v 48 D…ôndo, ¬ęy…õt ny…õ y…ĒŇčs…Ēm dis m…Ē y…Ēf…Ēfi, n…õnc nd…õ d…Ēnc…Ēf dis m…Ē d…Ēf…Ēnim…õ.¬Ľ\x - \xo 9:48 \xt Esayi 66.24\x* 
\v 49 Bawo nw…õ o nw…õ andek…Ēy…õk-y…õk…ôr k…Ē n…õnc da k…ôdusum p…ôm…Ē nt…õ aŇčy…õk-y…õk…ôr m…õr d…ôperi m…Ē.  
\v 50 M…õr paka p…Ēt…Ēt p…Ē. Mba k…Ē m…õr m…õnd…õnc…õ-…õ, ak'antam k…ôd…Ēkt…ôs…õ s…Ē mi-…õ? N…ôyi n…ônas…ôrka p…ôm…Ē m…õr, n…ôyin…õ p…ôforu k…Ē ak…Ē.¬Ľ 
\c 10  
\s1 Yesu k…ôt…ôks…õ k…Ēn teta k…ôcen…õn…õ ka an…õnc…õn…õ 
\p  
\v 1 Nt…õ Yesu …õy…õf…õ d…ôndo m…Ē, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē at…Ēf Ňča Yude ntende mokuru ma k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Yurd…õn. K…Ē k…ônay ka afum alar…ôm k…ôŇčk…Ē s…Ē k…ôloŇčkan…õ k…Ē k…ôs…ôk. K…Ē Yesu oncop k…ôt…ôks…õ Ňča, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē …Ēncy…Ē ti m…Ē.  
\v 2 K'aFarisi Ňčander bawo ŇčanafaŇč k…ôc…ôp…õ k…Ē towul d…ômoloku, k…Ē Ňčayif k…Ē: ¬ęSariy…õ s…ôwos…õ w…ôrkun k…ôce w…ôran k…Ēn ba?¬Ľ  
\v 3 K…Ē Yesu oloku Ňča: ¬ęC…ôke c…Ē Musa …õnasom nu-…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 4 K…Ē Ňčaloku: ¬ęNt…õ Musa …õnaloku m…Ē, a m…ôcic areka Ňčecen…õ w…ôran a m…ôdewur…õn…õ k…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 5 K…Ē Yesu oloku Ňča: ¬ęTeta b…ôk…ôc yonu yeyeŇčki t…Ē Musa …õnacic…õ tosom tant…õ.  
\v 6 Mba d…ôk…ôcop da doru k…Ē Kanu k…ôs…õl Ňča w…ôrkun k…Ē w…ôran.\x - \xo 10:6 \xt D…ôk…ôcop 1.27\x* 
\v 7 Ti t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ nt…õ w…ôrkun …õŇčsak…õ kas k…Ē k…õr…õ, p…ôsekt…ôrn…õ w…ôran k…Ēn m…Ē,  
\v 8 afum akaŇč…õ m…õr…ôŇč Ňčakaf…ôl…õ Ňčay…Ēn…õ t…õs…õm tin. Ti disr…õ Ňčay…Ēn…õ f…õ s…Ē afum m…õr…ôŇč, mba t…õs…õm tin.\x - \xo 10:8 \xt D…ôk…ôcop 2.24\x* 
\v 9 Ta fum p…ôgb…õy t…Ēk…Ē Kanu k…ônab…õmb…ôr…õn…õ m…Ē!¬Ľ  
\v 10 Nt…õ Ňčalukus d…õk…õr m…Ē, k…Ē ac…õps…õ …Ēn Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôyif…ôt k…Ē teta moloku mam…Ēk…Ē.  
\v 11 K…Ē Yesu oloku Ňča: ¬ęNw…õ ence w…ôran k…Ēn p…ôk…Ē p…ôn…õnc…õ w…ôl…Ēma m…Ē, d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ da w…ôsump…ôr dalak…Ē d'eyin…õ w…ôran w…ôkak…Ē.  
\v 12 K…Ē w…ôran ence wos, w…ôrkun w…ôl…Ēma p…ôn…õnc…õ k…Ē-…õ, nk…Ēn s…Ē dalak…Ē d'eyi.¬Ľ 
\s1 Yesu k…Ē awut 
\p  
\v 13 Afum Ňčanck…õr…õ Yesu awut af…õt nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ p…ôcdeŇč…ôr Ňča waca teta k…ôtolan…õ Ňča p…ôt…Ēt. Mba k…Ē ac…õps…õ …Ēn ŇčaŇčgb…ôŇč-gb…ôŇč…ôr Ňča.  
\v 14 Nt…õ Yesu …õn…ôŇčk ti m…Ē, k…Ē p…ônt…õl…õ k…Ē, k'oloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ôsak awut Ňčader nn…Ē iyi m…Ē, ta n…ôyams…ôr Ňča k…ôder, bawo, afum aŇč…õ Ňčayi p…ôm…Ē awut af…õt akaŇč…õ m…Ē, Ňča Ňčay…Ē d…õb…õ da Kanu.  
\v 15 Kance icloku nu: Nw…õ o nw…õ …Ēnt…Ēfayn…õ d…õb…õ da Kanu p…ôm…Ē wanf…õt m…Ē, …Ēf…Ēdek…Ēb…õr…õ di disr…õ.¬Ľ  
\v 16 K…Ē Yesu …õl…õk awut k'…Ēnt…Ēmp…ôr, k'…õy…õf…õ k…ôtolan…õ Ňča p…ôt…Ēt, p…ôcdeŇč Ňča waca d…ôs…ôbomp. 
\s1 Yesu k…Ē w…ôrkun w…ôka daka 
\p  
\v 17 Nt…õ Yesu osump…ôr d…Ēp…Ē k…ôk…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē fum w…ôl…Ēma …õy…õks…õ k'ende p…ôc…ôp…õ k…Ē suwu p…ôcyif k…Ē: ¬ęW…ôt…ôks…õ w…ôt…Ēt, c…ôke c…Ē p…ômar im k…ôy…Ē, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ is…Ēt…Ē kiyi w…ôyeŇč ka doru o doru m…Ē-…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 18 K…Ē Yesu eyif k…Ē: ¬ęTa ake t…Ē m…ôwen'em ‚ÄĻW…ôt…Ēt‚Äļ-…õ? Ali fum …Ēy…Ēn…õ f…õ w…ôt…Ēt, m…õn…õ Kanu sona gboŇč.  
\v 19 M…ônc…ôr…õ mosom ma Kanu: ‚ÄĻTa m…ôdif fum, ta m…ôsump…ôr dalak…Ē, ta m…ôkiy…õ, ta m…ôbaŇč…õ fum sede sa yem, ta m…ôdir fum, m…ôlel…ôs wisi k…Ē wiri.‚Äļ¬Ľ\x - \xo 10:19 \xt K…ôwur 20.12-16, \xt Sariy…õ 5.16-20\x* 
\v 20 K…Ē fum nw…õ oloku Yesu: ¬ęW…ôt…ôks…õ, ilel…ôs mam…Ēk…Ē f…ôp k…ôy…õf…õ is…Ēr…Ēf…õt…õ.¬Ľ  
\v 21 K…Ē Yesu …Ēm…Ēm…ôn k…Ē, k…Ē tet…Ēn t…Ēmb…Ēt k…Ē. K…Ē Yesu oloku k…Ē: ¬ęTes tin gboŇč tobut …ôm: M…ôk…Ē m…ôcam…ôs daka nd…õ m…ôy…Ē m…Ē f…ôp, m…ôs…ĒŇč p…ôsam pap…Ēk…Ē at…Ēy…Ē daka. K…Ē m…ôy…Ē ti-…õ m…ôndek…Ēs…Ēt…Ē daka d…õlar…ôm nde d…ôK…Ēm. K…Ē m…ôlip-…õ, m…ôder m…ôc…õps'em dar…ôŇč.¬Ľ  
\v 22 K…Ē dis d…õnd…õnc…õ fum nw…õ k…ône toloku ta Yesu, k'owur p…ôm…Ēncn…õ, bawo …õnay…Ē daka d…õlar…ôm.  
\v 23 K…Ē Yesu …Ēm…Ēm…ôn ac…õps…õ …Ēn k'oloku Ňča: ¬ęP…ôncuca aka daka k…ôb…õr…õ ka akip Ňča d…õb…õ da Kanu d…ônt…Ēf!¬Ľ  
\v 24 K…Ē p…ônciyan…õ ac…õps…õ …Ēn teta moloku mam…Ēk…Ē. Mba k…Ē Yesu …ĒŇčgb…Ēk…ôr…õ s…Ē: ¬ęAwut em, p…ôncuca k…ôb…õr…õ akip Ňča d…õb…õ da Kanu d…ônt…Ēf!  
\v 25 P…ôf…ôf…ôr…õn…õ y…Ēk…Ēm…õ k…ôb…õr…õ abi Ňča t…õs…õmb…õ p…ôtas w…ôka daka k…ôb…õr…õ ka akip Ňča d…õb…õ da Kanu d…ônt…Ēf.¬Ľ  
\v 26 K…Ē toloku tat…Ēk…Ē t…õnaŇčkan…õ k…ôwos…ôs ac…õps…õ …Ēn cusu, k…Ē Ňčayift…õn…õ: ¬ęAwa an'…õntam oŇč k…ôfis-…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 27 K…Ē Yesu …Ēm…Ēm…ôn Ňča, k'oloku: ¬ęAfum Ňčaf…Ētam ti, mba Kanu k…ôntam ti, bawo Kanu k…ôntam mes f…ôp.¬Ľ  
\v 28 K…Ē Piy…õr …õy…õf…õ k…ôloku k…Ē: ¬ęS…ôna s…ôsak ca f…ôp nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ s…ônc…ôm'am dar…ôŇč m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 29 K…Ē Yesu oloku k…Ē: ¬ęKance icloku nu: Fum eyi f…õ nw…õ …õsak…õ teta ina k…Ē Kibaru K…ôt…Ēt: K…ôl…Ē, aw…õnc, akir…õ, k…õr…õ, kas, awut k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti ant…Ēf-…õ,  
\v 30 w…ôkayi …ĒŇčs…Ēt…Ē t…õm tant…õ ayi m…Ē tasar tin ta yay…Ēk…Ē m…ôsak m…Ē f…ôp, k…ôy…õf…õ w…Ēl…Ē, aw…õnc, akir…õ, c…õr…õ, awut k…Ē nt…Ēf k…ôt…Ēr…ôs disr…õ, p…ôs…Ēt…Ē s…Ē kiyi w…ôyeŇč ka doru o doru t…õm tekiriŇč.  
\v 31 AkiriŇč alar…ôm Ňčandek…Ēy…Ēn…õ adar…ôŇč, k…Ē adar…ôŇč Ňčay…Ēn…õ akiriŇč.¬Ľ 
\s1 Yesu …õnd…ôŇčk s…Ē tamaas defi d…Ēn k…Ē k…ôf…Ēt…õ k…Ēn 
\p  
\v 32 D…Ēp…Ē Ňčanayi k…ôp…õ ka Yerusal…õm, k…Ē Yesu eyi Ňča kiriŇč, b…ôk…ôc y…õnal…õc…õ-l…õc…õ ac…õps…õ …Ēn, afum ak…Ē Ňčanac…ôm…õ Ňča dar…ôŇč m…Ē, Ňčanes…õ. K…Ē Yesu …õl…õk s…Ē Asom …Ēn aŇč…õ w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč, k'…õy…õf…õ k…ôl…Ēm…ôr Ňča t…Ēk…Ē tendes…Ēt…Ē k…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 33 K'oloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl im, Yerusal…õm ayi k…ôp…õ, andek…Ēl…õk Wan ka W…ôrkun pab…õr k…Ē aloŇčn…õ ap…ĒŇč k…Ē at…ôks…õ sariy…õ s'aSuyif d…ôwaca. K…Ē ŇčandeŇč…ôr k…Ē sariy…õ sa defi, Ňčab…õr k…Ē s…Ē at…Ēy…Ēn…õ aSuyif d…ôwaca,  
\v 34 akak…Ē Ňčafani k…Ē, Ňčayuks…ôr k…Ē lin, Ňčasut…õ k…Ē t…Ēr…ĒŇčk…Ēn, Ňčadif k…Ē. K…Ē mata maas mencep…ôr-…õ, p…ôf…Ēt…õ afi dac…Ē.¬Ľ 
\s1 Teyif ta Sak k…Ē IsaŇč 
\p  
\v 35 K…Ē awut a Sebede aŇč…õ m…õr…ôŇč Sak k…Ē IsaŇč Ňčander Ňčaloku Yesu: ¬ęW…ôt…ôks…õ, s…ôfaŇč m…ôy…Ēn…õ su nt…õ s…ôndetol'am m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 36 K…Ē Yesu eyif Ňča: ¬ęC…ôke c…Ē n…ôfaŇč a iy…Ēn…õ nu-…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 37 K…Ē Ňčaluks…õ Yesu: ¬ęM…ôwos…õ su w…ôkin k…ônd'am k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt k…Ē w…ôk…Ē k…ôca kam k…ômeriya nde n…Ēr…Ē da debeki dam.¬Ľ  
\v 38 K…Ē Yesu oloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ônc…ôr…õ f…õ nt…õ n…ôyi k…ôtola m…Ē. N…ôntam k…ôwos…õ k…ôt…Ēr…ôs p…ôm…Ē nk…õ ina indes…Ēt…Ē m…Ē ba? N…ôntam k…ôc…ôm…õ pucuy f…Ēr kiriŇč mp…õ pender k…ôb…ôp im m…Ē ba?¬Ľ  
\v 39 K…Ē Ňčaloku: ¬ęS…ôntam ti.¬Ľ K…Ē Yesu oloku Ňča: ¬ęAwa, n…ôna s…Ē n…ôndes…Ēt…Ē k…ôt…Ēr…ôs nk…õ indes…Ēt…Ē m…Ē, n…ôs…Ēt…Ē s…Ē pucuy p…Ēp…ĒŇč mp…õ pendeb…ôp im m…Ē.  
\v 40 Mba nt…õ t…Ēy…Ēn…õ k…ônd'em k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt k…Ē k…ôca k…ômeriya m…Ē, baf…Ē in'…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč ki. Afum ak…Ē am…õŇčk…õ mofo m…õnd…õ mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, Ňča Ňčay…Ē mi.¬Ľ  
\v 41 K…Ē p…ônt…õl…õ ac…õps…õ …Ēn aŇč…õ w…ôco nn…Ē Sak k…Ē IsaŇč Ňčayi m…Ē.  
\v 42 K…Ē Yesu ewe Ňča, k'oloku: ¬ęN…ônc…ôr…õ a ak…Ē anc…ôr…õ k…ôt…Ēmp…ôr d…õb…õ nde t…Ēf y…Ēl…Ēma m…Ē, Ňčantas…ôrn…õ afum aŇčan, s…Ēk…ôt s…Ē akiriŇč a t…Ēf yay…Ēk…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ēt…õn…õ k…ôtam afum aŇčan k…ôroŇč.  
\v 43 Mba tat…Ēk…Ē teyi f…õ nn…Ē n…ôna n…ôyi m…Ē, nt…õ t…Ēy…Ēn…õ m…Ē, nw…õ …õŇčfaŇč k…ôb…õk d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ nu dac…Ē m…Ē, p…ômar w…ôkayi p…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôb…ôc…õ konu,  
\v 44 nw…õ o nw…õ …õŇčfaŇč k…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôkiriŇč nu dac…Ē m…Ē, p…ômar p…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôcar ka f…ôp.  
\v 45 Wan ka W…ôrkun ender f…õ padeb…ôc…õ k…Ē, mba ender k…ôdeb…ôc…õ afum p…ôs…ĒŇč s…Ē kiyi k…Ēn w…ôyeŇč p…ôwurus k…ônay ka afum.¬Ľ 
\s1 Yesu …õntam…ôs w…ôt…Ēn…ôŇčk 
\p  
\v 46 K…Ē Ňčander Yeriko. Nt…õ Yesu …õncy…õf…õ Yeriko Ňčasol k…Ē ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč k…Ē k…ônay ka afum alar…ôm m…Ē, k…Ē w…ôtola w…ôt…Ēn…ôŇčk w…ôl…Ēma, Bartime wan ka Time p…ônd…õ d…Ēp…Ē k…ôs…ôk.  
\v 47 K…Ē Bartime ene a Yesu w…ôka Nasar…õt …Ēf…Ē, k'…õy…õf…õ k…ôkul…õ-kul…õ: ¬ęWan ka Dawuda, Yesu, m…ôy…Ēn'em n…Ēn…Ēf…Ēr!¬Ľ  
\v 48 K'afum alar…ôm ŇčaŇčgb…ôŇč-gb…ôŇč…ôr k…Ē a p…ôcaŇčk, mba p…ôcnaŇčkan…õ k…ôkul…õ-kul…õ: ¬ęWan ka Dawuda, m…ôy…Ēn'em n…Ēn…Ēf…Ēr!¬Ľ  
\v 49 K…Ē Yesu …õnc…ôm…õ k'oloku: ¬ęN…ôwe k…Ē.¬Ľ K…Ē Ňčawe w…ôt…Ēn…ôŇčk Ňčacloku k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôb…ôkn…õ, m…ôy…õf…õ, …õw'am.¬Ľ  
\v 50 K…Ē w…ôt…Ēn…ôŇčk …õl…ôm duma d…ôk…ôroŇč, k'oyokn…õ k…ôy…õf…õ, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē nde Yesu eyi m…Ē.  
\v 51 K…Ē Yesu eyif k…Ē: ¬ęC…ôke c…Ē m…ôfaŇč a iy…Ēn'am-…õ?¬Ľ K…Ē w…ôt…Ēn…ôŇčk oloku: ¬ęW…ôt…ôks…õ, iluks…ôrn…õ s…Ē k…ôn…ôŇčk!¬Ľ  
\v 52 K…Ē Yesu oloku k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôk…Ē, k…ôlaŇč kam k…ôntam…ôs …ôm.¬Ľ Gb…ôncana bab…Ēk…Ē, k'oluks…ôrn…õ s…Ē k…ôn…ôŇčk, k'…õnc…ôm…õ Yesu dar…ôŇč. 
\c 11  
\s1 Yesu …õmb…õr…õ Yerusal…õm 
\p  
\v 1 Nt…õ Yesu k…Ē ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč Ňčal…Ēt…ôrn…õ Yerusal…õm m…Ē, p…ôs…Ēr…Ēyi k…ôca ka B…õtfase k…Ē Betani ntende t…Ēr…Ē ta T…Ēk ya Olif k…ôs…ôk, k'osom ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč m…õr…ôŇč,  
\v 2 p…ôcloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ôk…Ē nde dare dand…õ n…ônt…õf…ôrn…õ m…Ē, k…Ē n…ôndena k…ôcb…õr…õ di-…õ, n…ôŇčk…Ēb…ôp di s…Ēfale s…ôf…õt ns…õ fum o fum …õntat…Ēnd…õ k…ôr…õsna k…ôroŇč m…Ē. N…ôsik…ôli si, n…ôk…õr'em.  
\v 3 K…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ fum p…ôyif nu: ‚ÄĻTa ake t…Ē n…ôŇčy…Ēn…õ ti-…õ?‚Äļ N…ôloku k…Ē: ‚ÄĻBawo Mariki …õfaŇč si. K'elip-…õ, …ĒŇčk…Ē nd…õk…ôl luks…õ si nn…Ē.‚Äļ¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 4 K'ac…õps…õ a Yesu dar…ôŇč aŇč…õ ŇčaŇčk…Ē, k…Ē Ňčamb…ôp s…Ēfale s…ôf…õt ns…õ pakot si dabaŇčka kumba k…ôs…ôk d…Ēp…Ē, k…Ē Ňčasik…ôli si.  
\v 5 Afum al…Ēma aŇč…õ Ňčanayi d…ônda m…Ē Ňčayif Ňča: ¬ęC…ôke c…Ē n…ôyi k…ôy…Ē-…õ? Ta ake t…Ē n…ôŇčsik…ôl…õ s…Ēfale sas…Ēk…Ē-…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 6 K…Ē Ňčaloku t…Ēk…Ē Yesu …õnaloku Ňča m…Ē, k'akak…Ē Ňčawos…õ Ňča k…ôsik…ôli si.  
\v 7 K…Ē ŇčaŇčken…õ Yesu s…Ēfale ns…õ, k…Ē ŇčadeŇčs…ôr si suma s…ôŇčan sak…ôroŇč, k…Ē Yesu …õnd…õ si k…ôroŇč.  
\v 8 K'afum alar…ôm Ňčamper-per…õ k…Ē suma s…ôŇčan sak…ôroŇč d…Ēp…Ē, k…Ē al…Ēma Ňčamboc…õ k…Ē bat d…Ēp…Ē ny…õ Ňčanac…õp d…ôkulum m…Ē.  
\v 9 Afum ak…Ē Ňčanck…Ēt k…Ē tekiriŇč, k…Ē ak…Ē Ňčanac…ôm…õ k…Ē dar…ôŇč m…Ē Ňčackul…õ-kul…õ: 
\q1 ¬ęHosana!\f + \fr 11:9 \fq Hosana\ft  = toloku ta kusu ka Arame t…Ē, it'oloku ¬ęO Mariki, m…ôyac su!¬Ľ\f* Kanu k…ôpoc…õ p…ôt…Ēt nw…õ ender…õn…õ tewe ta Mariki m…Ē!\x - \xo 11:9 \xt Yabura 118.25-26\x* 
\q1  
\v 10 Kanu k…ôpoc…õ p…ôt…Ēt d…õb…õ da kas kosu Dawuda nd…õ deyi k…ôder m…Ē! 
\q1 Hosana p…ôlel peyi Kanu nk…õ k…ôyi d…ôK…Ēm m…Ē!¬Ľ 
\m  
\v 11 K'…õmb…õr…õ Yerusal…õm nde k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu. Nt…õ elip k…ôm…Ēm…ôn c…ôs…ôk c…Ēn m…Ē, k…Ē pibi pender, Yesu k…Ē ac…õps…õ …Ēn w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč Ňčawur k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Betani. 
\s1 Yesu ontolan…õ k…ôt…Ēk p…ôl…õc 
\p  
\v 12 D…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk nt…õ Ňčacwur Betani m…Ē, dor d…õnay…Ē Yesu.  
\v 13 K'…õn…ôŇčk p…ôb…Ēl…õ k…ôt…Ēk ka yokom ya fik k…ôkumpt…ôr b…Ēp…ôr, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē k…ôm…Ēm…ôn k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a …ĒŇčs…Ēt…ôr ki pedi-…õ, mba nt…õ …õmb…ôp ki m…Ē, …õnan…ôŇčk f…õ pokom o pokom m…õn…õ b…Ēp…ôr, bawo baf…Ē t…õm tokom ta fik t…õnayi.  
\v 14 K…Ē Yesu oloku k…ôt…Ēk: ¬ęTa fum o fum p…ôdi s…Ē yokom ya m…ôna!¬Ľ K…Ē ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč Ňčane ti. 
\s1 Yesu nde k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu 
\p  
\v 15 K…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Yerusal…õm. Nt…õ Yesu …õmb…õr…õ k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu m…Ē, k'…õy…õf…õ k…ôb…õl…ôs acam…ôs f…ôp k…Ē ak…Ē Ňčancway d…ôndo k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč m…Ē. K'…õŇčgbal…ôs m…õsa ya as…ôkp…ôr p…ôsam k…Ē s…ôc…Ēm sa acam…ôs ntantoriya,  
\v 16 …õnawos…õ f…õ nw…õ o nw…õ k…ôsar…õ-sar…õ ca p…ôcep…ôr…õn…õ d…ôndo k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč disr…õ.  
\v 17 K…Ē Yesu …õnt…ôks…õ Ňča p…ôcloku: ¬ęBaf…Ē Kanu k…ôloku d…ôYecic…ôs: ‚ÄĻAndewe k…ôl…Ē kem d…ôk…ôtola Kanu da afum a t…Ēf ya doru f…ôp.‚Äļ\x - \xo 11:17 \xt Esayi 56.7\x* Mba n…ôna n…ôŇčkaf…ôli ki t…Ēgb…Ēk…õn…õ ta calbante.¬Ľ\x - \xo 11:17 \xt Yeremy 7.11\x* 
\v 18 AloŇčn…õ ap…ĒŇč k…Ē at…ôks…õ sariy…õ s'aSuyif Ňčane k…Ē dim, k…Ē Ňčant…õn t…Ēk…Ē Ňčantam k…ôdif k…Ē m…Ē. Ňäancnes…õ k…Ē, bawo cusu c…ônawos afum f…ôp teta m…õt…ôks…õ m…Ēn.  
\v 19 Nt…õ d…Ēf…Ēy d…õmb…ôp m…Ē, Yesu k…Ē ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč Ňčawur dare. 
\s1 Yesu k…Ē k…ôt…Ēk k…ôwos…ôr…õn…õ 
\p  
\v 20 B…ôtb…ôt, nt…õ Ňčayi k…ôcep…ôr m…Ē, k…Ē ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč Ňčan…ôŇčk k…ôt…Ēk ka fik k…ôwos…ôr…õn…õ haŇč nt…õnt…ôl.  
\v 21 K…Ē Piy…õr …õnc…õm-c…õmn…õ t…Ēk…Ē t…õnacep…ôr m…Ē, k'oloku Yesu: ¬ęW…ôt…ôks…õ, m…ôm…Ēm…ôn k…ôt…Ēk ka fik nk…õ m…ônatolan…õ p…ôl…õc m…Ē, k…ôwos…ôr…õn…õ.¬Ľ  
\v 22 K…Ē Yesu oloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ôgb…õk…ôr k…ôlaŇč konu Kanu.  
\v 23 Kance icloku nu: Nw…õ oŇčloku t…Ēr…Ē tant…õ: ‚ÄĻM…ôy…õf…õ nn…Ē m…ôk…Ē m…ôl…ômn…õ d…ôk…ôba,‚Äļ k…Ē m…ônt…Ēnes…ôr-nes…ôr d…õb…ôk…ôc, mba m…ôlaŇč a t…Ēk…Ē m…ôloku m…Ē teŇčyi-…õ, aŇčy…Ēn'am ti.  
\v 24 It'…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ nt…õ iloku nu: Nt…õ o nt…õ t…Ē n…ôloku k…ôtola Kanu disr…õ m…Ē, n…ôlaŇč a n…ôŇčs…Ēt…Ē ti, aŇčy…Ēn…õ nu ti.  
\v 25 K…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ n…ôndetola, p…ôy…Ēn…õ n…ôm…õŇčk…õ fum m…õt…õl…õ-…õ, n…ôŇčaŇčn…õn…õ k…Ē, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Kas konu nk…õ k…ôyi nde d…ôK…Ēm m…Ē, k…ôŇčaŇčn…õn…õ s…Ē n…ôna p…ôl…õc ponu.  
\v 26 [\f + \fr 11:26 \ft Yecic…ôs yokur y…Ēl…Ēma yendeŇč…ôr moloku mam…õ: ¬ęMba k…Ē n…ôna n…ônt…ĒŇčaŇčn…õn…õ ak…Ē-…õ, Papa konu nw…õ eyi nde d…ôk…Ēm m…Ē …Ēf…ĒŇčaŇčn…õn…õ s…Ē n…ôna k…ôciya konu.¬Ľ\f*] 
\s1 Deke d…õb…õ da Yesu d…õŇčy…õf…õ-…õ? 
\p  
\v 27 K…Ē Yesu Ňčalukus Yerusal…õm k…Ē ac…õps…õ …Ēn, nt…õ Ňčanck…Ēt nde k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu m…Ē, aloŇčn…õ ap…ĒŇč, at…ôks…õ sariy…õ s'aSuyif k…Ē abeki a d…Ēt…Ēf Ňčander Ňčab…ôp Yesu  
\v 28 k…ôdeyif k…Ē: ¬ęK…ôtam k…ôre k…Ē m…ôŇčy…Ēn…õ mam…õ-…õ? An'…Ēs…ĒŇč …ôm k…ôtam nk…õ m…ôŇčy…Ēn…õ mes mam…õ m…Ē-…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 29 K…Ē Yesu oloku Ňča: ¬ęTeyif tin gboŇč t'indeyif nu, n…ôluks'em ti, ina s…Ē iloku nu k…ôtam nk…õ iŇčy…Ēn…õ mam…õ m…Ē.  
\v 30 K…ôgb…ôt d…ôromun ka SaŇč d…ôk…Ēm k…ôncy…õf…õ ba, ka nda afum? N…ôluks'em toloku.¬Ľ  
\v 31 Mba k…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôgb…õk…ôl…õn…õ taŇčan: ¬ęK…Ē s…ôluks…õ nd…õk…ôl a d…ôk…Ēm k…ôgb…ôt k…Ēn k…ônay…õf…õ-…õ, eŇčyif su: ‚ÄĻTa ake t…Ē n…ônat…ĒlaŇč…õ SaŇč-…õ?‚Äļ  
\v 32 K…Ē s…ôloku a nda afum k…ôncy…õf…õ-…õ, apayo! P…ôy…Ē w…õyw…õy d…ônda!¬Ľ Ňäancnes…õ k…ônay ka afum, bawo f…ôp f…ônac…ôr…õ a SaŇč sayib…õ yati s'…õnay…Ēn…õ.  
\v 33 K…Ē Ňčaluks…õ Yesu moloku: ¬ęS…ônc…ôr…õ f…õ.¬Ľ K…Ē Yesu nk…Ēn oloku Ňča s…Ē: ¬ęIna s…Ē, if…Ēloku nu k…ôtam nk…õ iŇčy…Ēn…õ mam…õ m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\c 12  
\s1 Totubc…õn…õ ta ab…ôc Ňčgb…ĒŇčk…ôl…Ē ya w…õn al…õc 
\p  
\v 1 K…Ē Yesu …õy…õf…õ k…ôlok-lok…ôr Ňča d…ôtotubc…õn…õ: ¬ęFum w…ôl…Ēma …õnab…Ēf Ňčgb…ĒŇčk…ôl…Ē ya w…õn. K…Ē fum nw…õ …Ēs…Ēn…õ yi saŇčka haŇč k'…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôr, k'…õŇčkay d…ôk…ôf…Ēc…ôs da wi, k'…õnc…ômb…ôr tetek tobum…õ. Nt…õ elip m…Ē, k'…Ēs…ĒŇč y…õb…ôc ya ab…Ēf Ňča Ňčgb…ĒŇčk…ôl…Ē ya w…õn yay…Ēk…Ē afum al…Ēma, Ňčat…ôŇčn…õ k…Ē akak…Ē k…ôcs…ĒŇč k…Ē k…ôway, k…Ē nk…Ēn owur k'…ĒŇčk…Ē mar…ônt.  
\v 2 Nt…õ t…õm tepim t…õmb…ôp m…Ē, k…Ē fum nw…õ osom w…ôcar nda ab…Ēf a Ňčgb…ĒŇčk…Ēl…Ē ya w…õn, k…ôk…ĒbaŇč yokom ya w…õn y…Ēk…Ē p…ômar pas…ĒŇč k…Ē k…ôway k…Ēn m…Ē.  
\v 3 K…Ē ab…ôc a Ňčgb…ĒŇčk…ôl…Ē ya w…õn Ňčasump…ôr k…Ē, k…Ē Ňčasut, k…Ē Ňčasak, k'olukus waca w…Ēs…Ēk…ôr.  
\v 4 K…Ē w…ôka Ňčgb…ĒŇčk…ôl…Ē nw…õ osom s…Ē w…ôcar w…ôl…Ēma, k…Ē ab…ôc a Ňčgb…ĒŇčk…ôl…Ē ya w…õn aŇč…õ Ňčasut s…Ē w…ôkak…Ē domp, k…Ē Ňčalap…ôs k…Ē d…ôm…Ēl…Ēm…ôs.  
\v 5 K…Ē mariki mm…õ m…ĒŇčgb…Ēk…ôr…õ s…Ē k…ôsom w…ôl…Ēma, k…Ē ab…Ēf aŇč…õ Ňčasump…ôr w…ôkak…Ē k…Ē Ňčandif. Ab…ôc akaŇč…õ Ňčanasut alar…ôm, Ňčacdif alar…ôm.  
\v 6 Wan k…Ēn nw…õ …Ēmb…Ēt…ôr m…Ē, sona s'…õnac…ôm…õ k…Ē oŇč. K'osom w…ôlp…ôs w…ôkak…Ē nn…Ē Ňčayi m…Ē, p…ôcloku: ‚ÄĻŇäaŇčk…Ēlel…ôs w…ôkaw…õ, wan kem …Ēf…Ē!‚Äļ  
\v 7 K…Ē ab…ôc a Ňčgb…ĒŇčk…ôl…Ē ya w…õn aŇč…õ Ňčalok…õn…õ: ‚ÄĻW…ôl…õk k…Ēn k…õ …Ēf…Ē, w…ôkaw…õ! N…ôder, padif k…Ē, k…õ k…ôndey…Ēn…õ kosu.‚Äļ  
\v 8 K…Ē Ňčasump…ôr k…Ē, k…Ē Ňčandif, k…Ē ŇčaŇčgbal k…ôbel k…Ēn saŇčka tadar…ôŇč.¬Ľ  
\v 9 K…Ē Yesu eyif Ňča: ¬ęC…ôke c…Ē w…ôka Ňčgb…ĒŇčk…ôl…Ē endey…Ē-…õ? W…ôka Ňčgb…ĒŇčk…ôl…Ē ender p…ôdif…ôt ab…ôc akak…Ē, p…ôl…õk ab…ôc al…Ēma, p…ôs…ĒŇč Ňča y…õb…ôc ya Ňčgb…ĒŇčk…ôl…Ē y…Ēn.  
\v 10 N…ônakaraŇč f…õ Yecic…ôs Yosoku yay…õ ba?: ‚ÄĻTogbu mp…õ ac…ômb…ôr k…ôl…Ē Ňčanace m…Ē, p…õnader p…Ēy…Ēn…õ oŇč togbu p…Ēt…Ēt, pa dac…Ē.  
\v 11 D…ôMariki t…õy…õf…õ, tes t…Ē nt…õ tenciyan…õ su d…ôf…Ēr m…Ē.‚Äļ¬Ľ\x - \xo 12:11 \xt Yabura 118.22-23\x* 
\p  
\v 12 K…Ē akiriŇč aSuyif ŇčafaŇč k…ôsump…ôr Yesu, mba k…Ē Ňčanes…õ k…ônay ka afum. Ňäanac…ôr…õ a tetaŇčan t…Ē Yesu …õnalok…õn…õ totubc…õn…õ tat…Ēk…Ē. K…Ē Ňčasak Yesu, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē. 
\s1 AkiriŇč aSuyif ŇčafaŇč k…ôc…ôp…õ Yesu towul 
\p  
\v 13 K…Ē akiriŇč aSuyif Ňčasom nn…Ē Yesu eyi m…Ē aFarisi k…Ē afum a Herodu al…Ēma, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňčac…ôp…õ Yesu towul, Ňčasump…ôr k…Ē d…ômoloku m…Ē.  
\v 14 K…Ē akak…Ē Ňčander Ňčaloku k…Ē: ¬ęW…ôt…ôks…õ, s…ônc…ôr…õ a m…ôlomp, m…ôf…Ēnes…õ k…ôl…ôs…ôr tewe, m…ôf…Ēkiti fum t…õn…ôŇčk t…Ēn, d…Ēp…Ē da Kanu yati d…Ē m…ônt…ôks…õ afum d…ôkance. Awa, sariy…õ s…ôwos…õ su k…ôs…ĒŇč Sesar\f + \fr 12:14 \fq Sesar\ft  tewe t…Ē, nt…õ anas…ĒŇč nw…õ o nw…õ …Ēt…Ēmp…ôr d…õb…õ da t…Ēf ya Rom m…Ē.\f* w…ôb…õ w…ôka t…Ēf ya Rom dut ba, ka ta s…ôs…ĒŇč k…Ē di?¬Ľ  
\v 15 Nt…õ Yesu …õnac…ôr…õ Ňča k…ôy…Ēn…õ abaŇč…õn…õ k…ôlomp m…Ē, k'oluks…õ Ňča: ¬ęTa ake t…Ē n…ôŇčwak…ôs em-…õ? N…ôk…õr'em gb…ôleŇč bin ba p…ôsam, ider im…Ēm…ôn.¬Ľ  
\v 16 K…Ē ŇčaŇčk…õr…õ k…Ē gb…ôleŇč bin. K'eyif Ňča: ¬ęAlulu Ňča ana Ňč…Ē ŇčaŇč…õ k…Ē yecic…ôs yay…õ-…õ?¬Ľ K…Ē afum aŇč…õ Ňčaloku: ¬ęYa Sesar w…ôb…õ w…ôka Rom y…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 17 K…Ē Yesu oloku Ňča: ¬ęAwa, n…ôs…ĒŇč Sesar p…Ēk…Ē p…Ēy…Ēn…õ p…Ēn m…Ē, k…Ē Kanu s…Ē p…Ēk…Ē p…Ēy…Ēn…õ p…Ēn m…Ē.¬Ľ K…Ē cusu c…ôwos Ňča p…ôp…ĒŇč tet…Ēn. 
\s1 Teyif ta k…ôf…Ēt…õ afi dac…Ē 
\p  
\v 18 K'aSadisi\f + \fr 12:18 \fqa ASadisi\ft  = k…ôgba ka afum aSuyif aŇč…õ Ňčanc…õm-c…õmn…õ a k…ôy…õf…õ defi k…ôyi f…õ, m…õl…õk…õ meyi f…õ, y…ĒŇčk k…Ē arkifin yeyi f…õ m…Ē. M…ôm…Ēm…ôn s…Ē Asom 23.8\f* aŇč…õ Ňčaloku a fum …Ēf…Ēy…õf…õ defi m…Ē, Ňčander Ňčayif Yesu:  
\v 19 ¬ęW…ôt…ôks…õ, nt…õ t…Ē Musa …õnacic…õ su: ‚ÄĻK…Ē fum efi ta …Ēy…Ē wan, mba p…ôsak w…ôran-…õ, p…ômar w…õnc ka w…ôfi p…ôl…õk w…ôc…ôbok…ôra w…ôkak…Ē p…ôn…õnc…õ, p…ôs…ĒŇč w…õnc w…ôfi yuruya.‚Äļ  
\v 20 Aw…õnc aŇča cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč Ňčanayi. K…Ē w…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē …õn…õnc…õ, k'efi …õsak f…õ yuruya.  
\v 21 K…Ē w…ôka m…õr…ôŇč …õn…õnc…õ, nk…Ēn s…Ē k'efi …õsak f…õ yuruya. It…Ē p…ônayi w…õnc w…ôka maas,  
\v 22 ali w…ôkin aw…õnc aŇča akaŇč…õ cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč …õnasak f…õ yuruya. Nt…õ Ňčalip k…ôfis-fis m…Ē, k…Ē w…ôran s…Ē efi.  
\v 23 Ti disr…õ, k…Ē d…Ēs…Ēk d…õy…õf…õ da afi dendeb…ôp, an'endey…Ē w…ôran-…õ? Bawo afum akaŇč…õ cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč Ňčanan…õnc…õ k…Ē!¬Ľ  
\v 24 K…Ē Yesu oloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ôn…ôŇčk it'…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ nt…õ n…ônciyan…õ m…Ē. N…ônc…ôr…õ f…õ Yecic…ôs Yosoku, n…ônc…ôr…õ f…õ s…Ē f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr fa Kanu.  
\v 25 K'afi Ňčandef…Ēt…õ afi dac…Ē-…õ, Ňčaf…Ēde Ňčacn…õnc…õn…õ, Ňčandeyi p…ôm…Ē m…õl…õk…õ mm…õ meyi Kanu k…ôs…ôk m…Ē.  
\v 26 K…ôcloku a fum endef…Ēt…õ afi dac…Ē, n…ôŇčkaraŇč f…õ buk ba Musa ba? Nt…õ Kanu k…ônaloku Musa nde d…õr…ônt…ôm m…Ē: ‚ÄĻIn'…Ēy…Ēn…õ Kanu ka Abraham, Kanu ka Siyaka, Kanu ka Yakuba!‚Äļ\x - \xo 12:26 \xt K…ôwur 3.6\x* 
\v 27 Baf…Ē Kanu ka afi k'…Ēy…Ēn…õ, mba ka ayi w…ôyeŇč. N…ôna n…ôsoln…õ f…õ kance!¬Ľ 
\s1 Tosom t…Ēk…Ē telel…õ t…õtas mosom f…ôp m…Ē 
\p  
\v 28 K…Ē w…ôt…ôks…õ sariy…õ s'aSuyif w…ôl…Ēma, nw…õ …õnane Ňča sim Ňčacgb…õk…ôl…õn…õ m…Ē, …õn…ôŇčk a Yesu olok-lok…ôr Ňča belbel, k'ender p…ôcyif Yesu: ¬ęTosom tere t…õb…õk d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ mosom f…ôp dac…Ē-…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 29 K…Ē Yesu oloku k…Ē: ¬ęTosom tayi t…Ēy…Ēn…õ: ‚ÄĻM…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl Yisrayel! Mariki, Kanu kosu sona gboŇč s'…Ēy…Ēn…õ Mariki.  
\v 30 M…ôb…Ēt…ôr…õ Mariki Kanu kam ab…ôk…ôc Ňčam f…ôp, af…Ēk…ôl Ňčam f…ôp, m…õc…õmc…õmn…õ mam k…Ē s…Ēk…ôt sam f…ôp.‚Äļ\x - \xo 12:30 \xt Sariy…õ 6.4-5\x* 
\v 31 T…Ēc…Ēnc ta ti t…Ēy…Ēn…õ: ‚ÄĻM…ôb…Ēt…ôr w…õnc …ôm p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē m…ômb…Ēt…ôrn…õ m…Ē.‚Äļ\x - \xo 12:31 \xt ALewy 19.18\x* Tosom t…Ēl…Ēma teyi f…õ nt…õ t…õmb…õk t…õtas mam…õ m…õr…ôŇč m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 32 K…Ē w…ôt…ôks…õ sariy…õ nw…õ oloku k…Ē: ¬ęTentes…õ, W…ôt…ôks…õ, m…ôloku ti kance disr…õ: A Mariki sona s…Ēn gboŇč s'…Ēy…Ēn…õ Kanu, a w…ôl…Ēma eyi f…õ k…Ē p…ônt…Ēy…Ēn…õ nk…Ēn-…õ,  
\v 33 m…ôb…Ēt…ôr k…Ē ab…ôk…ôc Ňčam f…ôp, k…Ē dosoku domp dam f…ôp, k…Ē s…Ēk…ôt sam f…ôp, m…ôb…Ēt…ôr w…õnc …ôm p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē m…ômb…Ēt…ôrn…õ m…Ē. Mosom mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ēy…Ē d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ m…õtas y…Ēc…Ēl ny…õ anc…Ēf…õ Mariki m…Ē k…Ē yoloŇčn…õ y…Ēl…Ēma f…ôp.¬Ľ  
\v 34 Nt…õ Yesu …õn…ôŇčk a w…ôt…ôks…õ sariy…õ w…ôkaw…õ oloku t…Ēk…Ē p…ômar m…Ē, k…Ē Yesu oloku k…Ē: ¬ęM…ômb…Ēl…õ f…õ k…ôb…õr…õ akip Ňča d…õb…õ da Kanu d…ônt…Ēf.¬Ľ Ali fum …õnab…ôkn…õ f…õ s…Ē k…ôyif…ôt k…Ē toloku t…Ēl…Ēma. 
\s1 Krist k…Ē Dawuda 
\p  
\v 35 Yesu p…ôct…ôks…õ nde k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu: ¬ęC…ôke c…Ē at…ôks…õ sariy…õ s'aSuyif Ňčantam k…ôloku a Krist\f + \fr 12:35 \fq Krist\ft  = W…ôb…õ nw…õ Kanu k…ôy…õk-y…õk m…Ē, W…ôy…õk-y…õk ka Kanu \f* wan ka Dawuda gb…ôc…ôr…ôm …Ēf…Ē-…õ?  
\v 36 Amera Ňäecempi Ňč…õnas…ĒŇč…õ nk…Ēn Dawuda yati k…ôloku nt…õ: ‚ÄĻMariki Kanu oloku Mariki mem: ¬ęM…ôder m…ônd'em nn…Ē k…ôca kem k…ôt…Ēt haŇč iclip k…ôboc ater…õn…õ am w…õc…ôk wam d…ônt…Ēf.¬Ľ‚Äļ\x - \xo 12:36 \xt Yabura 110.1\x* 
\v 37 Nk…Ēn Dawuda yati ewe w…ôsom w…ôka Kanu ‚ÄĻMariki‚Äļ, c…ôke c…Ē Mariki …õntam k…ôy…Ēn…õ wan ka Dawuda-…õ?¬Ľ K…ônay ka afum alar…ôm k…ôncc…ôŇčk…ôl Yesu p…ôbotu disr…õ. 
\s1 Yesu oloku k…ônay ka afum k…ôk…õmb…ôrn…õ ka at…ôks…õ sariy…õ 
\p  
\v 38 Yesu oncloku k…ônay ka afum d…ôm…õt…ôks…õ m…Ēn: ¬ęN…ôk…õmb…ôrn…õ at…ôks…õ sariy…õ s'aSuyif, Ňčamb…Ēt…ôr k…ôcac…õn…õ suma s…ôp…ĒŇč, pacyif Ňča k…ôyif k…ôlel mofo mm…õ amb…ôps…õn…õ m…Ē,  
\v 39 pacs…ĒŇč Ňča s…ôc…Ēm s…ôkiriŇč sa d…ôk…ôtola Kanu da aSuyif, pacs…ĒŇč Ňča d…ôk…ônd…õ d'ab…õ mofo medi yeri d…ôc…ôsata.  
\v 40 ŇäacbaŇčs…ôr ac…ôbok…ôra daka daŇčan, Ňčacb…Ēls…õ sali nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ pagb…õk…ôr…õ Ňča m…Ē. Andek…Ēkiti Ňča kiti k…ôyeŇčki.¬Ľ 
\s1 K…ôpoc…õ ka w…ôc…ôbok…ôra w…ôt…Ēy…Ē daka 
\p  
\v 41 D…ôndo k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu, Yesu p…ônd…õ p…ôt…õf…ôrn…õ kaŇčk…ôra, p…ôgb…ôtn…õ nt…õ k…ônay ka afum k…ômb…õr ki p…ôsam m…Ē. Aka daka alar…ôm Ňčancb…õr ki p…ôsam p…õlar…ôm.  
\v 42 K…Ē w…ôc…ôbok…ôra w…ôt…Ēy…Ē daka w…ôl…Ēma ender p…ôboc f…ôr…õŇčk m…õr…ôŇč nf…õ f…ônapic…õ d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ m…Ē.  
\v 43 K…Ē Yesu ewe ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč k'oloku Ňča: ¬ęKance icloku nu: W…ôc…ôbok…ôra w…ôt…Ēy…Ē daka w…ôkaw…õ ompoc…õ p…ôtas ak…Ē f…ôp aŇč…õ Ňčamboc p…ôsam kaŇčk…ôra disr…õ m…Ē.  
\v 44 Bawo, pecern…õ paŇčan p…Ē ak…Ē f…ôp Ňčamboc, mba nk…Ēn, k…ôt…Ēy…Ē k…Ēn daka disr…õ omboc p…Ēk…Ē …Ēy…Ē gb…ôc…ôr…ôm pedi m…Ē .¬Ľ 
\c 13  
\s1 Yesu oloku a andel…ôs…ôr k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu 
\p  
\v 1 Nt…õ Yesu owur k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu disr…õ m…Ē, k…Ē w…ôc…õps…õ k…Ēn dar…ôŇč w…ôkin oloku k…Ē: ¬ęW…ôt…ôks…õ, m…ôm…Ēm…ôn masar m…õpat m…Ēt…Ēt, m…ôm…Ēm…ôn w…Ēl…Ē w…ôp…ĒŇč wa k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu!¬Ľ  
\v 2 K…Ē Yesu oloku k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôŇčn…ôŇčk w…Ēl…Ē w…Ēp…ĒŇč waw…õ! Tasar p…Ēf…ĒdedeŇčs…õ tasar k…ôroŇč nn…Ē, mp…õ ant…ĒdewuŇč m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\s1 P…ôl…õc k…Ē k…ôt…Ēr…ôs 
\p  
\v 3 Nt…õ Yesu …õnd…õ nde t…Ēr…Ē ta T…Ēk ya Olif p…ôt…õf…ôrn…õ k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu m…Ē, Piy…õr, Sak, IsaŇč k…Ē And…ôre Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôyif…ôt k…Ē Ňčab…Ēk…ôr…õ:  
\v 4 ¬ęM…ôloku su ake t…õm t…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē tendeyi-…õ? T…õgb…õk…ôr…õ tere tendement…ôr k…ôlar…õ ka mes mam…õ m…ôloku m…Ē f…ôp-…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 5 K…Ē Yesu …õy…õf…õ k…ôloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ôk…õmb…ôrn…õ ta fum o fum p…ôs…ĒŇč…õ nu k…ôs…Ēl…õ!  
\v 6 Afum alar…ôm Ňčandeder ŇčacbaŇč…õn…õ k…ôb…ôc…õ tewe tem, Ňčacloku nu: ‚ÄĻIn'…Ēf…Ē, w…ôsom w…ôka Kanu!‚Äļ Ňäandetal…ôr k…ônay ka afum alar…ôm.  
\v 7 K…Ē n…ôndene pacloku teta k…ôwan k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti, pacfor teta ki-…õ, ta n…ônes…õ! M…õn…õ mes mam…Ēk…Ē meyi, mba t…Ēf…Ēdey…Ēn…õ k…ôr…õsna k…ôlip ka doru de.  
\v 8 Bawo afum a at…Ēf Ňč…Ēl…Ēma Ňčandey…õf…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē afum a at…Ēf Ňčocuru, d…õb…õ d…õy…õf…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē d…õb…õ. Ant…Ēf k…ôyikc…õ k…Ē dor yendeyi mofo m…õlar…ôm. Mam…Ēk…Ē f…ôp mendeyi p…ôm…Ē k…ôcop ka pucuy pa dokomb…ôra.  
\v 9 N…ôk…õmb…ôrn…õ n…ônas…ôrka nt…õ t…õntam k…ôb…ôp nu m…Ē. Andekek…ôr…õ nu d…ôŇčkiti d'aSuyif, andesut nu d…ôk…ôtola Kanu da aSuyif d…õlar…ôm. N…ôndeloku t…Ēk…Ē n…ônc…ôr…õ tetem m…Ē akiriŇč a s…ôdare s…ôp…ĒŇč k…Ē ab…õ a t…Ēf al…Ēma f…Ēr kiriŇč.  
\v 10 M…õn…õ pad…ôŇčk…ôr k…ôr…õsna Kibaru K…ôt…Ēt afum a t…Ēf ya doru f…ôp.  
\v 11 K'andekek…ôr…õ nu k…ôk…Ēb…õr Ňča d…ôwaca-…õ, ta n…ônes…õ t…Ēk…Ē n…ôŇčk…Ēloku m…Ē, mba n…ôloku t…Ēk…Ē aŇčk…Ēs…ĒŇč nu gb…ôncana bab…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, bawo baf…Ē n…ôn'endek…Ēlok-loku, mba Amera Ňäecempi Ňča Kanu.  
\v 12 W…õnc wendek…Ēs…ĒŇč w…õnc padif. Tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ē kas k…ôndek…Ēs…Ēy…Ē wan k…Ēn. Awut Ňčandek…Ēc…ôm…õ akomb…ôra aŇčan d…õb…ôk…ôc, Ňčas…ĒŇč Ňča padif.  
\v 13 F…ôp f…ôndeter nu teta tewe tem, mba nw…õ endeb…ôkn…õ ti haŇč mes mam…Ēk…Ē melip m…Ē, Kanu k…ôndeyac k…Ē.¬Ľ 
\s1 P…ôyikyik p…õl…ôs…ôr p…ôp…ĒŇč mp…õ Mariki enter m…Ē 
\p  
\v 14 ¬ęK…Ē n…ônden…ôŇčk p…ôyikyik p…õl…ôs…ôr p…ôp…ĒŇč mp…õ Mariki enter m…Ē,\x - \xo 13:14 \xt Daniyel 9.27; 11.31; 12.11\x* p…õnd…õ nn…Ē p…ônt…Ēmar pi k…ôyi m…Ē, a afum ak…Ē Ňčandeyi Yude m…Ē p…ômar Ňčay…õks…õ Ňčap…õ m…Ēr…Ē k…ôroŇč. P…ômar w…ôkaraŇč ka buk bamb…õ p…ôc…ôr…õ tant…õ!  
\v 15 Nw…õ eŇčyi dabaŇčka m…Ē, ta p…ôb…õr…õ k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn disr…õ k…ôk…Ēl…õk paka.  
\v 16 Nw…õ eŇčyi dal…õ m…Ē, ta p…ôlukus nde nd…Ēr…Ēn k…ôk…Ēl…õk duma d…Ēn.  
\v 17 Pucuy pere p…Ē tendey…Ēn…õ ab…õk…ôs, k…Ē aŇč…õ Ňčande Ňčacm…õs…ôr d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē m…Ē!  
\v 18 N…ôtola Kanu ta pucuy pap…Ēk…Ē peder d…õr…ôŇč.  
\v 19 Bawo mataka mam…Ēk…Ē m…ĒŇčy…Ēn…õ mataka ma k…ôt…Ēr…ôs, nk…õ k…ônt…Ēy…Ē k…ôwur…õn…õ k…ôy…õf…õ nt…õ Kanu k…ôlomp…ôs doru m…Ē haŇč nd…õk…ôl, fum o fum af…Ēs…Ēt…Ēr…ôs p…ôm…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē.  
\v 20 Mba Mariki Kanu p…ônat…Ēbel…ôr mataka mam…Ēk…Ē-…õ, k'ali fum …Ēf…Ēdek…Ēfis. Mba …õnabel…ôr mataka mam…Ēk…Ē teta aŇč…õ …õnay…õk-y…õk m…Ē.  
\v 21 K…Ē fum w…ôl…Ēma oloku nu: ‚ÄĻM…ôm…Ēm…ôn: Krist eyi nn…Ē,‚Äļ ‚ÄĻM…ôm…Ēm…ôn: Eyi nde,‚Äļ ta n…ôlaŇč w…ôkayi.  
\v 22 Bawo abaŇč…õn…õ k…ôy…Ēn…õ Krist k…Ē sayib…õ sa yem Ňčandewur doru. Ňäade Ňčacy…Ē m…õgb…õk…ôr…õ k…Ē mes m…õw…õy-w…õy nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ, k…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ Ňčactam-…õ, Ňčatal…ôr ak…Ē Kanu k…ônay…õk-y…õk m…Ē.  
\v 23 N…ôk…õmb…ôrn…õ belbel, iloku nu mes mam…õ ta m…õntab…ôp-…õ!¬Ľ 
\s1 K…ôder ka Wan ka W…ôrkun 
\p  
\v 24 ¬ęMba mataka mam…Ēk…Ē, k…Ē pucuy pap…Ēk…Ē pencep…ôr-…õ, p…ôndey…Ē gb…ôr…ôp, Ňčof Ňč…Ēf…Ēdes…Ēmar,  
\v 25 c…Ēs c…ôndet…õmp…õn…õ k…ôy…õf…õ d…ôk…Ēm, f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr fa k…Ēm f…ôndeyikc…õ.\x - \xo 13:25 \xt Esayi 13.10; 34.4\x* 
\v 26 Awa, anden…ôŇčk Wan ka W…ôrkun p…ôcder d…ôk…ôp k…Ē f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr f…ôlar…ôm k…Ē n…Ēr…Ē da debeki d…Ēn.  
\v 27 Endesom m…õl…õk…õ …Ēn d…ôm…Ēmp…Ēmp…Ē ma doru f…ôp k…ôloŇčka ka aŇč…õ …õnay…õk-y…õk m…Ē d…ômoŇčkubut maŇčk…ôl…õ ma d…ôK…Ēm k…Ē ant…Ēf.¬Ľ 
\s1 K…ôt…ôks…õ nk…õ k…ôt…Ēk ka fik k…ôs…ĒŇč m…Ē 
\p  
\v 28 ¬ęN…ôt…ôk…ôs totubc…õn…õ nt…õ k…ôt…Ēk ka fik k…ôment…ôr m…Ē: K…Ē wara wa ki w…õcaŇčk w…õl…õŇčk-…õ, n…ôc…ôr…õ a k…ôt…ôn k…ôl…Ēt…ôrn…õ.  
\v 29 N…ôna s…Ē, k…Ē n…ônden…ôŇčk mes mam…Ēk…Ē mecder-…õ, n…ôc…ôr…õ a Wan ka W…ôrkun …Ēl…Ēt…ôrn…õ yati.  
\v 30 Kance icloku nu: D…õt…õmp dand…õ d…Ēf…Ēcep…ôr ta mes mam…õ f…ôp meyi-…õ.  
\v 31 K…Ēm k…Ē ant…Ēf yendes…Ēl…õ, mba moloku mem m…Ēf…Ēdes…Ēl…õ.¬Ľ 
\s1 Fum o fum …Ēf…Ēc…ôr…õ t…õm nt…õ Mariki endeder m…Ē 
\p  
\v 32 ¬ęNt…õ t…Ēy…Ēn…õ ta d…Ēs…Ēk, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti, ta t…õm nt…õ doru dendelip m…Ē, fum o fum …õnc…ôr…õ f…õ ti, ali m…õl…õk…õ mm…õ meyi d…ôk…Ēm m…Ē f…ôp, ali wan, m…õn…õ Papa sona gboŇč …õc…ôr…õ ti.  
\v 33 N…ôk…õmb…ôrn…õ, ta n…ôd…ĒŇč…ôs, bawo n…ônc…ôr…õ f…õ t…õm nt…õ tendeyi m…Ē.  
\v 34 P…ôndeyi p…ôm…Ē nt…õ w…ôrkun endek…Ē mar…ônt, p…ôsak k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn, p…ôs…ĒŇč acar …Ēn nw…õ o nw…õ y…õb…ôc y…Ēn, p…ôsom w…ôbum k…ôk…õmb…ôrn…õ kumba.  
\v 35 N…ôna s…Ē n…ôk…õmb…ôrn…õ, bawo n…ônc…ôr…õ f…õ t…õm nt…õ w…ôka k…ôl…Ē endeder m…Ē: T…õntam k…ôy…Ēn…õ d…Ēfana, c…õkc…õkana, d…Ēs…Ēkana k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ b…ôtb…ôtana.  
\v 36 Ta p…ôder p…ôb…ôp nu n…ôcdir…õ.  
\v 37 Tant…õ iŇčloku nu m…Ē, iŇčloku ti f…ôp, n…ôk…õmb…ôrn…õ!¬Ľ 
\c 14  
\s1 Ab…õ Ňčasek…õ Yesu t…õŇčk…ônd…ôm 
\p  
\v 1 C…ôsata ca K…ôcep…ôr ka M…õl…õk…õ medif k…Ē ka C…ôcom c…ôt…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôl lebin p…ômar c…ôyi k…Ē mata m…õr…ôŇč mencep…ôr-…õ. AloŇčn…õ ap…ĒŇč k…Ē at…ôks…õ sariy…õ s'aSuyif Ňčanct…õn k…ôsump…ôr Yesu c…ôp…ônp…ôn disr…õ, Ňčadif k…Ē.  
\v 2 Bawo Ňčancloku a ta pasump…ôr k…Ē d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôsata, ta tedes…ĒŇč…õ p…ôyamayama pedeyi afum dac…Ē. 
\s1 W…ôran osop Yesu labund…õ d…ôromp 
\p  
\v 3 Nt…õ Yesu …õnayi Betani m…Ē, ndena Sim…ĒŇč w…ôcun…õ sen, k…Ē w…ôran w…ôl…Ēma …õmb…õr…õ t…õt…ôŇčn…õ Ňčacdi yeri. W…ôran nw…õ p…ôt…Ēmp…ôr t…Ēk…Ēb…Ē pa alabat…ôr\f + \fr 14:3 \fq T…Ēk…Ēb…Ē pa alabat…ôr\ft  = T…Ēk…Ēb…Ē mp…õ anclomps…õ tasar pefer p…õpat. AŇčwe tasar p…Ēt…Ēt mp…õ ¬ęalabat…ôr¬Ľ.\f* p…õlar…õ labund…õ da nar t…õp, labund…õ deyeŇčki k…ôway. K'osuncu t…Ēk…Ēb…Ē mp…õ, k'oloŇčs…ôr labund…õ nd…õ f…ôp Yesu d…ôromp.  
\v 4 K…Ē p…ônt…õl…õ afum al…Ēma, k…Ē Ňčayifn…õ: ¬ęTa ake t…Ē …õl…ôs…ôr…õ-l…ôs…ôr…õ labund…õ dand…õ-…õ?  
\v 5 Anatam di k…ôcam…ôs haŇč p…ôsam gb…ôleŇč masar maas, pas…ĒŇč pi at…Ēy…Ē daka.¬Ľ K…Ē p…ônt…õl…õ Ňča nn…Ē w…ôran nw…õ eyi m…Ē.  
\v 6 Mba k…Ē Yesu oloku: ¬ęN…ôce k…Ē! Ta ake t…Ē n…ôc…ôm…õn…õ k…Ē dar…ôŇč-…õ? T…Ēy…Ē t…Ēt…Ēt t'…Ēy…Ē nn…Ē ina iyi m…Ē.  
\v 7 At…Ēy…Ē daka, Ňčayi nu dac…Ē t…õm f…ôp, n…ôntam k…ôy…Ēn…õ Ňča p…ôt…Ēt t…õm nt…õ o nt…õ n…ôŇčfaŇč m…Ē. Mba ina, n…ôf…Ēdey'em t…õm f…ôp.  
\v 8 ∆Üy…Ē t…Ēk…Ē …õntam m…Ē. OnuŇčk…õn…õ k…ôsop im labund…õ k…ôlomp…ôs ka k…ôbel kem a pacwup ki.  
\v 9 Kance icloku nu: Nn…Ē o nn…Ē anded…ôŇčk Kibaru K…ôt…Ēt doru dand…õ k…Ērk…Ēr m…Ē, aŇčloku s…Ē t…Ēy…Ē t…Ēt…Ēt ta w…ôran w…ôkaw…õ k…ôc…õm-c…õm…ôs ka doru.¬Ľ 
\s1 Yudas …õfaŇč k…ôs…ĒŇč Yesu ab…õ a aloŇčn…õ 
\p  
\v 10 Yudas w…ôka dare da Keriyot, nw…õ …õnayi ac…õps…õ a Yesu dar…ôŇč aŇč…õ w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč dac…Ē m…Ē, …ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôb…ôp ab…õ a aloŇčn…õ, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ p…ôb…õr Yesu Ňča d…ôwaca m…Ē.  
\v 11 Nt…õ aloŇčn…õ Ňčanc…ôŇčk…ôl moloku m…Ēn m…Ē, k…Ē p…ômb…Ēt Ňča, k…Ē Ňčaloku k…ôs…ĒŇč k…Ē p…ôsam. Yudas p…ôct…õn t…Ēy…Ē nt…õ endek…Ēb…õr Yesu Ňča d…ôwaca m…Ē. 
\s1 Yesu eyi k…ôdi yeri ya Pak k…Ē ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč 
\p  
\v 12 D…Ēs…Ēk d…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē da k…ôsata ka C…ôcom c…ôt…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôl lebin, d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ ancloŇčn…õ Ňčkesiya ya K…ôcep…ôr ka M…õl…õk…õ medif m…Ē, k…Ē ac…õps…õ a Yesu dar…ôŇč Ňčayif k…Ē: ¬ęDeke m…ôfaŇč s…ôk…Ēlomps'am yeri ya k…ôsata ka K…ôcep…ôr ka M…õl…õk…õ medif-…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 13 K…Ē Yesu osom ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč m…õr…ôŇč, k'oloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ôk…Ē dare, n…ôŇčk…Ēn…ôŇčk w…ôrkun p…ôsar…õ apamp…õ Ňča domun p…ôder, k…ôdefayn…õ nu. N…ôc…ôm…õ k…Ē dar…ôŇč,  
\v 14 nde …ĒŇčk…Ēb…õr…õ m…Ē, n…ôloku w…ôka k…ôl…Ē: ‚ÄĻW…ôt…ôks…õ oloku: Deke d…ôk…ôl…Ē deyi nd…õ indedi yeri ya k…ôsata ka K…ôcep…ôr ka M…õl…õk…õ medif k…Ē ac…õps…õ em dar…ôŇč-…õ?‚Äļ  
\v 15 Endek…Ēment…ôr nu d…ôk…ôl…Ē d…Ēp…ĒŇč k…ôl…Ē darenc, palomp…ôs di belbel ca f…ôp yeyi di. D…ôndo n…ôŇčk…Ēlomps…õ su yeri ya k…ôsata kaŇčk…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 16 K…Ē ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč ŇčaŇčk…Ē, k…Ē Ňčamb…õr…õ dare, k…Ē Ňčamb…ôp ca f…ôp p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē …õnaloku Ňča ti m…Ē. K…Ē Ňčalomp…ôs yeri ya k…ôsata kaŇčk…Ē.  
\v 17 K…Ē d…Ēf…Ēy d…õmb…ôp, k'ender k…Ē ac…õps…õ …Ēn w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč.  
\v 18 T…õm nt…õ Ňčanand…õ d…õm…õsa Ňčacdi yeri m…Ē, k…Ē Yesu oloku: ¬ęKance icloku nu: W…ôkin nu dac…Ē, nw…õ eyi k…ôdi yeri k…Ē ina m…Ē, endeb…õr im ater…õn…õ em d…ôwaca.¬Ľ  
\v 19 K…ôm…Ēncn…õ disr…õ k…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôyif…ôt k…Ē: ¬ęIn'…Ēf…Ē ba?¬Ľ  
\v 20 K…Ē Yesu oloku Ňča: ¬ęW…ôkin n…ôna akaŇč…õ w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč dac…Ē, nw…õ s…ômb…õr waca dap din disr…õ k…ôdi yeri m…Ē.  
\v 21 Wan ka W…ôrkun endefi, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē ancic ti m…Ē. Mba p…ôl…õc pere peyi w…ôrkun w…ôkaw…õ endeb…õr Wan ka W…ôrkun ater…õn…õ …Ēn d…ôwaca m…Ē! K…ônat…Ēkom ka w…ôrkun w…ôkaw…õ k…ônatam k…ôtes…õ k…Ē!¬Ľ 
\s1 Mariki k…ôpaŇčn…õ k…Ēn yeri, k…ôpus k…Ē ac…õps…õ …Ēn 
\p  
\v 22 Nt…õ Ňčancdi yeri m…Ē, k…Ē Yesu …õl…õk k…ôcom, k'eyif Kanu barka, k'entepi ki k'…Ēs…ĒŇč…ôs Ňča p…ôcloku: ¬ęN…ôbaŇč, dis dem d…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 23 K'…õl…õk s…Ē t…Ēmb…ôl ta w…õn, nt…õ elip k…ôyif Kanu barka m…Ē, k'…Ēs…ĒŇč…ôs Ňča k…Ē Ňčamun f…ôp faŇčan.  
\v 24 K'oloku Ňča: ¬ęMecir mem m…Ē, mm…õ aloŇč teta k…ôcaŇč…ôs danapa da Kanu k…Ē k…ônay ka afum m…Ē.  
\v 25 Kance icloku nu: If…Ēs…Ēmun w…õn haŇč d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ indegb…Ēk…ôr…õ s…Ē k…ômun wi, nde d…õb…õ da Kanu m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 26 Nt…õ Ňčalip k…ôleŇč…ôs meleŇč mokor-kor…õ Kanu m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčawurn…õ ntende k…ôca ka t…Ēr…Ē ta T…Ēk ya Olif. 
\s1 Yesu oloku a Piy…õr endece k…ôc…ôr…õ k…Ēn 
\p  
\v 27 K…Ē Yesu oloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ôna akaŇč…õ f…ôp n…ôndelukus im dar…ôŇč, bawo Yecic…ôs Yosoku yoloku: ‚ÄĻIndesut w…ôk…õk, Ňčkesiya y…õsams…ôr.‚Äļ\x - \xo 14:27 \xt Sakary 13.7\x* 
\v 28 Mba k'indef…Ēt…õ afi dac…Ē-…õ, indek…Ēkar nu Kalile.¬Ľ  
\v 29 K…Ē Piy…õr oloku k…Ē: ¬ęAli f…ôp f…ôlukus …ôm dar…ôŇč, ina if…Ēlukus …ôm dar…ôŇč.¬Ľ  
\v 30 K…Ē Yesu oloku k…Ē: ¬ęKance iclok'…ôm: Pibi pamp…õ yati, m…ôndegb…õk…ôl k…ômaas a m…ônc…ôr…õ f'em a kicipi k…ôccam tam…õr…ôŇč.¬Ľ  
\v 31 Mba Piy…õr p…ôcgb…õk…ôl ti p…ôp…ĒŇč: ¬ęAli s…ôcfi k…Ē m…ôna, if…Ēgb…õk…ôl a inc…ôr'am.¬Ľ Ac…õps…õ a Yesu dar…ôŇč ak…Ē f…ôp toloku tin tayi t…Ē Ňčancloku. 
\s1 Yesu …õsali Ketsemane 
\p  
\v 32 K…Ē Ňčamb…ôp k…ôfo nk…õ aŇčwe Ketsemane m…Ē, k'oloku ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč: ¬ęN…ônd…õ nn…Ē t…õm nt…õ iŇčk…Ētola Kanu m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 33 K'…õl…õk Piy…õr, Sak k…Ē IsaŇč. K…Ē k…ônes…õ k…ôp…ĒŇč k…ôncop k…ôsump…ôr Yesu k…Ē ab…ôk…ôc Ňč…õl…õc…õ-l…õc…õ k…Ē.  
\v 34 K'oloku Ňča: ¬ęAb…ôk…ôc Ňč…õnaŇčkan…õ k…ôd…õnc'em p…ôm…Ē ifi. N…ôyi nn…Ē, ta n…ôdir…õ!¬Ľ  
\v 35 Nt…õ Yesu …Ēmb…Ēl…õn…õ Ňča p…ôpic m…Ē, k'…õmb…õlk…ôr k…ôc…ôp tobu d…ônt…Ēf, k'ontola nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ, k…Ē t…õntam k…ôyi-…õ, t…õm tocuca tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ēb…Ēl…õ k…Ē.  
\v 36 P…ôcloku: ¬ęAba, Papa, m…ôn'…õtam mes f…ôp, m…ôb…Ēl…õn'em t…Ēmb…ôl pa k…ôt…Ēr…ôs pamp…õ. Ti disr…õ, baf…Ē t…Ēk…Ē ifaŇč m…Ē de, mba nt…õ m…ôna m…ôfaŇč m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 37 K…Ē Yesu ender p…ôb…ôp ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč Ňčacdir…õ. K'eyif Piy…õr: ¬ęSim…ĒŇč, k…ôdir…õ k…Ē m…ônd…õ ba? M…ôntam f…õ k…ôt…Ēdir…õ ali dec din?  
\v 38 Ta n…ôdir…õ, n…ôtola Kanu nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ta n…ômb…õr…õ k…ôwak…ôs disr…õ m…Ē. P…ômbas mera yonu k…ôy…Ē p…ôt…Ēt, mba n…ôy…Ē f…õ s…Ēk…ôt k…ôy…Ē ti.¬Ľ  
\v 39 K…Ē Yesu …Ēmb…Ēl…õ s…Ē, p…ôcgb…Ēk…ôr…õ totola Kanu tin tat…Ēk…Ē.  
\v 40 K…Ē Yesu olukus, k'ender p…ôb…ôp ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč Ňčacd…ĒŇč…ôs, nt…õ f…Ēr y…õnal…Ēl Ňča m…Ē, Ňčanac…ôr…õ f…õ toloku nt…õ ŇčaŇčluks…õ k…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 41 K…Ē Yesu …ĒŇčgb…Ēk…ôr…õ s…Ē k…ôder tamaas k'…õŇčgb…ôŇč-gb…ôŇč…ôr Ňča: ¬ęN…ôndir…õ s…Ē, k…ôŇčes…ôm k…Ē n…ônd…õ! Telip! N…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl: T…õm t…õmb…ôp, amb…õr Wan ka W…ôrkun aciya d…ôwaca.  
\v 42 N…ôy…õf…õ, paŇčk…Ēn, nw…õ eyi k…ôb…õr im afum d…ôwaca m…Ē, …Ēl…Ēt…ôrn…õ.¬Ľ 
\s1 As…Ēdar Ňčasump…ôr Yesu 
\p  
\v 43 Yesu p…ôs…Ēr…Ēlok-loku, k…Ē Yudas nw…õ …õnayi ac…õps…õ a Yesu aŇč…õ w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč dac…Ē m…Ē, ender p…ôsol…õ k…ônay ka afum aŇč…õ Ňčanat…Ēmp…ôr-t…Ēmp…ôr sakma, k…Ē t…Ēk yosutn…õn…õ m…Ē. AloŇčn…õ ap…ĒŇč, at…ôks…õ sariy…õ s'aSuyif k…Ē abeki Ňčanasom Ňča.  
\v 44 Yudas nw…õ …õncb…õr Yesu ater…õn…õ …Ēn d…ôwaca m…Ē, …õnas…ĒŇč as…Ēdar t…õm…ônc…õ nt…õ: ‚ÄĻNw…õ iŇčk…Ēcup m…Ē, nk…Ēn …Ēf…Ē w…ôkak…Ē. N…ôsump…ôr k…Ē, n…ôkek…ôr…õ, n…ôgb…õk…ôr…õ k…Ē belbel.‚Äļ  
\v 45 Gb…ôncana bab…Ēk…Ē k…Ē Yudas ender, k'…Ēl…Ēt…ôrn…õ Yesu, k'ewe k…Ē: ¬ęW…ôt…ôks…õ,¬Ľ k'oncup k…Ē.  
\v 46 K…Ē afum akak…Ē Ňčant…ôps…ôr Yesu waca, k…Ē Ňčasump…ôr k…Ē.  
\v 47 W…ôkin ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč dac…Ē owur…õ dakma d…Ēn, k'…õnc…õp w…ôcar ka w…ôloŇčn…õ w…ôp…ĒŇč al…ôŇč…ôs, k'eŇčgbinti Ňči.  
\v 48 K…Ē Yesu oloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ôwur k…ôdesump…ôr im, n…ôt…Ēmp…ôr-t…Ēmp…ôr sakma k…Ē t…Ēk yosutn…õn…õ p…ôm…Ē nt…õ iŇčy…Ēn…õ kalbante m…Ē.  
\v 49 D…Ēs…Ēk o d…Ēs…Ēk incyi nu dac…Ē ict…ôks…õ nde k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu, ta n…ônder n…ôsump…ôr im-…õ. Mba tat…Ēk…Ē teŇčyi nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Yecic…ôs Yosoku y…õlar…õ m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 50 K…Ē asol …Ēn f…ôp Ňčasak Yesu, k…Ē Ňčay…õks…õ.  
\v 51 W…ôt…õmp w…ôl…Ēma …õnac…ôm…õ Yesu dar…ôŇč, p…ôgbal…ôrn…õ k…ôloto gb…ôc…ôr…ôm. K…Ē Ňčasump…ôr k…Ē,  
\v 52 mba w…ôkak…Ē …õnasalp…ôr Ňča, k'…õsak…ôr…õn…õ Ňča k…ôloto k…ôŇčk…Ē …õnagbal…ôrn…õ m…Ē, k'…õy…õks…õ p…ôwur fos. 
\s1 Yesu f…Ēr ya aboc kiti ap…ĒŇč 
\p  
\v 53 K…Ē ŇčaŇčkek…ôr…õ Yesu ndena w…ôloŇčn…õ w…ôp…ĒŇč. Ab…õ a aloŇčn…õ f…ôp, abeki k…Ē at…ôks…õ sariy…õ s'aSuyif Ňčamb…ôps…õn…õ.  
\v 54 Piy…õr …õnc…ôm…õ Ňča dar…ôŇč, p…ôcm…Ēm…ôn ti p…ôb…Ēl…õ, haŇč nde k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka w…ôloŇčn…õ w…ôp…ĒŇč, nde abaŇčka disr…õ. P…ônd…õ k…Ē abum, p…ôcsay…õ n…õnc k…ôs…ôk.  
\v 55 AloŇčn…õ ap…ĒŇč k'aboc kiti aSuyif f…ôp Ňčanct…õn sede ns…õ s…ônak…ĒbaŇč…õ Ňča moloku m…Ēk…Ē Ňčanak…ĒdeŇč…õ Yesu, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ padif k…Ē m…Ē, mba Ňčanas…Ēt…Ē f…õ.  
\v 56 Afum alar…ôm Ňčancbonc…õ k…Ē yem, mba yem yay…Ēk…Ē yoncsur…õn…õ f…õ.  
\v 57 Al…Ēma Ňčaccop k…ôbonc…õ k…Ē yem ny…õ:  
\v 58 ¬ęS…ône k…Ē p…ôcloku: ‚ÄĻIndel…ôs…ôr k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu kaŇčk…õ waca wa fum wolomp…ôs m…Ē, mata maas disr…õ ic…ômb…ôr k…ôl…Ēma nk…õ waca wa fum w…Ēnt…Ēdelomp…ôs m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 59 Ali yem yay…Ēk…Ē y…õnasur…õn…õ f…õ k…ôy…Ēn…õ ka sede.  
\v 60 K…Ē w…ôloŇčn…õ w…ôp…ĒŇč …õy…õf…õ afum dac…Ē, k'eyif Yesu: ¬ęM…ôf…Ēluks…õ su t…Ēl…Ēm o t…Ēl…Ēm ba? C…ôke c…Ē m…ôŇčloku teta moloku ma sede mm…õ akaŇč…õ Ňčambonc am m…Ē?¬Ľ  
\v 61 Mba k…Ē Yesu …õncaŇčk, oluks…õ f…õ toloku nt…õ o nt…õ. K…Ē w…ôloŇčn…õ w…ôp…ĒŇč eyif k…Ē s…Ē: ¬ęM…ôn'…Ēy…Ēn…õ Krist, Wan ka Kanu nk…õ aŇčkor-koru m…Ē ba?¬Ľ  
\v 62 K…Ē Yesu oloku: ¬ęIn'…Ēf…Ē. N…ônden…ôŇčk Wan ka W…ôrkun p…ônd…õ k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt ka Kanu nk…õ k…ôntam mes f…ôp m…Ē, p…ôcder n…Ēr…Ē da debeki d…Ēn disr…õ d…ôk…ôp ka d…ôK…Ēm.¬Ľ  
\v 63 K…Ē w…ôloŇčn…õ w…ôp…ĒŇč …õwali-wali yamos y…Ēn k'eyif: ¬ęSede s…ôre s…Ē p…ômar payif-…õ?  
\v 64 N…ône t…Ēk…Ē …Ēl…Ēm…ôs Kanu m…Ē. C…ôke c…Ē n…ônc…õm-c…õmn…õ-…õ?¬Ľ K…Ē f…ôp f…ôloku a p…ômar padif k…Ē.  
\v 65 K…Ē afum al…Ēma Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôyuks…ôr Yesu lin, Ňčackump k…Ē k…ôro, Ňčacsut k…Ē Ňčkulma, Ňčacloku: ¬ęAwa Sayib…õ, m…ôloku su an'osut …ôm-…õ?¬Ľ K…Ē abum ŇčambaŇč Yesu k…Ē Ňčafer…ôs k…Ē waca d…ôkanca. 
\s1 Piy…õr ence k…ôc…ôr…õ Yesu 
\p  
\v 66 T…õm nt…õ Piy…õr …õnayi tant…Ēf nde saŇčka disr…õ m…Ē, k…Ē w…ôcar w…ôyec…ôra w…ôkin w…ôka w…ôloŇčn…õ w…ôp…ĒŇč ender.  
\v 67 Nt…õ …õn…ôŇčk Piy…õr p…ôcsay…õ m…Ē, k'…õŇčgb…ôtn…õ k…Ē, k'oloku k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôna s…Ē Yesu w…ôka Nasar…õt n…ônayi.¬Ľ  
\v 68 K…Ē Piy…õr …õŇčgb…õk…ôl ti p…ôcloku: ¬ęInc…ôr…õ f…õ, inc…ôr…õ f…õ nt…õ m…ôna m…ôfaŇč k…ôloku m…Ē!¬Ľ K'owur k…ôk…Ēnd…õ saŇčka tadar…ôŇč, nde d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ. K…Ē kicipi k…ôncam.\f + \fr 14:68 \ft Y…Ēgb…Ēk…ôr…õ ya yecic…ôs yokur y…Ēl…Ēma y…Ēy…Ē f…õ: ¬ęK…Ē kicipi k…ôncam.¬Ľ\f* 
\v 69 K…Ē w…ôcar w…ôran nw…õ …õn…ôŇčk k…Ē, k'…ĒŇčgb…Ēk…ôr…õ s…Ē ti k…ôloku ak…Ē Ňčanayi di m…Ē: ¬ęW…ôl…Ēma …Ēf…Ē w…ôkaw…õ s…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 70 Mba k…Ē Piy…õr …õŇčgb…õk…ôl s…Ē. P…ôwon f…õ, aŇč…õ Ňčanayi di m…Ē, Ňčaloku s…Ē Piy…õr: ¬ęS…ôlaŇč ti, afum akaŇč…õ w…ôkin m…ôy…Ēn…õ, bawo m…ôna s…Ē w…ôka Kalile m…ôy…Ēn…õ.¬Ľ  
\v 71 K…Ē Piy…õr …õy…õf…õ k…ôd…õr…ôm: ¬ęKanu k…ôt…Ēr…ôs im k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a k…ôyem…õ k'ind…õ-…õ! Ind…õr…ôm a inc…ôr…õ f…õ fum w…ôkaw…õ n…ôŇčle m…Ē!¬Ľ  
\v 72 Gb…ôncana bab…Ēk…Ē k…Ē kicipi k…ôncam s…Ē tam…õr…ôŇč. K…Ē Piy…õr …õnc…õm-c…õmn…õ toloku t…Ēk…Ē Yesu …õnaloku k…Ē m…Ē: ¬ęM…ôndegb…õk…ôl k…ômaas a m…ônc…ôr…õ f'em a kicipi k…ôccam tam…õr…ôŇč.¬Ľ K…Ē Piy…õr …õy…õf…õ k…ôbok. 
\c 15  
\s1 Yesu f…Ēr ya Pilat kiriŇč 
\p  
\v 1 Nt…õ b…ôtb…ôt b…õmb…ôp m…Ē, aloŇčn…õ ap…ĒŇč k…Ē abeki, at…ôks…õ sariy…õ k…Ē aboc kiti aSuyif f…ôp, ŇčaloŇčkan…õ k…ôk…Ēt…ôŇčn…õ nt…õ andey…Ē Yesu m…Ē. Nt…õ Ňčalip k…ôkot k…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčamb…õr k…Ē Pilat d…ôwaca.  
\v 2 K…Ē Pilat eyif k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôn'…Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôb…õ ka aSuyif ba?¬Ľ K…Ē Yesu oluks…õ k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôn'oloku ti.¬Ľ  
\v 3 AloŇčn…õ ap…ĒŇč Ňčanat…Ēmp…ôr…õ k…Ē meyems…õn…õ m…õlar…ôm.  
\v 4 K…Ē Pilat eyif k…Ē s…Ē: ¬ęM…ôf…Ēloku nt…õ o nt…õ? M…ône mam…õ Ňčambonc am m…Ē f…ôp!¬Ľ  
\v 5 Mba Yesu …õnaluks…õ f…õ k…Ē s…Ē toloku nt…õ o nt…õ, ti t…õnawos…ôs Pilat kusu p…ôp…ĒŇč. 
\s1 AŇčkiti Yesu k…ôfi 
\p  
\v 6 Awa k…ôren o k…ôren k…ôsata ka K…ôcep…ôr ka M…õl…õk…õ Medif, Pilat …õncsak…õ afum y…õŇč…ôn w…ôyi d…ôbili w…ôkin nw…õ ŇčaŇčfaŇč m…Ē.  
\v 7 T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē fum w…ôl…Ēma …õnayi d…ôbili pacwe k…Ē Barabas nw…õ anab…õr d…ôbili teta k…ôdif fum, nt…õ Ňčanay…õf…õ k…ôyeŇčk…ôr ab…õ a d…Ēt…Ēf s…ôbomp m…Ē.  
\v 8 K…Ē k…ônay ka afum k…ômp…õ, k…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôyif…ôt a pay…Ēn…õ Ňča t…Ēk…Ē amb…Ēt k…ôy…Ēn…õ Ňča m…Ē.  
\v 9 K…Ē Pilat eyif Ňča: ¬ęIsak…ôr…õ nu w…ôb…õ w…ôka aSuyif ba?¬Ľ  
\v 10 Bawo Pilat …õnac…ôr…õ a k…ôraca ka aloŇčn…õ ap…ĒŇč k…ônas…ĒŇč…õ Ňča k…ôl…õk Yesu Ňčab…õr k…Ē d…ôwaca.  
\v 11 Mba k…Ē aloŇčn…õ ap…ĒŇč ŇčagbiŇč…ôr k…ônay ka afum, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ pasak…õ Ňča y…õŇč…ôn Barabas m…Ē.  
\v 12 K…Ē Pilat …ĒŇčgb…Ēk…ôr…õ s…Ē: ¬ęC…ôke c…Ē n…ôfaŇč a iy…Ē nw…õ n…ôŇčwe w…ôb…õ ka aSuyif m…Ē-…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 13 K…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôkul…õ-kul…õ: ¬ęM…ôcaŇč k…Ē d…ôt…Ēk y…õp…ômp…ôl!¬Ľ  
\v 14 K…Ē Pilat eyif Ňča: ¬ęP…ôl…õc pere p'…Ēy…Ē-…õ?¬Ľ Mba k…Ē afum ŇčanaŇčkan…õ k…ôkul…õ-kul…õ p…ôp…ĒŇč: ¬ęM…ôcaŇč k…Ē d…ôt…Ēk y…õp…ômp…ôl!¬Ľ  
\v 15 K…Ē Pilat …õnc…õm-c…õmn…õ k…ôy…Ē t…õfaŇč ta k…ônay ka afum: K'…õsak…õ Ňča y…õŇč…ôn Barabas. Nt…õ elip k…ôsom pasut…õ Yesu t…Ēr…ĒŇčk…Ēn m…Ē, k'…õmb…õr k…Ē afum d…ôwaca a pacaŇč k…Ē d…ôt…Ēk y…õp…ômp…ôl. 
\s1 As…Ēdar Ňčafani Yesu 
\p  
\v 16 K…Ē as…Ēdar ŇčaŇčkek…ôr…õ Yesu nde abaŇčka Ňča k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Pilat, k…Ē Ňčawe d…õŇčgb…õŇčk dad…Ēk…Ē f…ôp.  
\v 17 K'as…Ēdar Ňčamb…õr Yesu duma d'ab…õ deyim, k…Ē ŇčandeŇč…ôr k…Ē d…ôromp aŇčgb…ĒŇčk…ôl…Ē Ňča b…õŇčk yodu.  
\v 18 K…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôfani k…Ē Ňčacyif: ¬ęIŇčyif …ôm, w…ôb…õ ka aSuyif.¬Ľ  
\v 19 K…Ē Ňčasut…õ Yesu domp k…ôgbo, k…Ē Ňčayuk…ôr k…Ē lin, Ňčanut suwu teta k…ôfani k…Ē.  
\v 20 Nt…õ Ňčalip k…ôfani k…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčawur…õ k…Ē duma d'ab…õ deyim k…Ē Ňčamb…õr k…Ē yamos y…Ēn. K…Ē ŇčaŇčkek…ôr…õ k…Ē k…ôk…ĒcaŇč k…Ē d…ôt…Ēk y…õp…ômp…ôl. 
\s1 AncaŇč Yesu d…ôt…Ēk y…õp…ômp…ôl 
\p  
\v 21 K…Ē as…Ēdar Ňčawe fum w…ôl…Ēma nw…õ …õnay…õf…õ dal…õ m…Ē, pacwe w…ôkayi Sim…ĒŇč w…ôka dare da Sir…õn, papa ka Al…õksand…ôr k…Ē Rifis, k…ôk…ĒgbaŇčn…õ t…Ēk y…õp…ômp…ôl ny…õ anak…Ē k…ôcaŇč Yesu m…Ē.  
\v 22 K…Ē ŇčaŇčkek…ôr…õ Yesu k…ôfo nk…õ aŇčwe Kolkota m…Ē, it…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē ¬ęK…ôfo ka K…ômb…õmb…ôl…õ¬Ľ.  
\v 23 K…Ē as…Ēdar ŇčafaŇč k…ôs…ĒŇč Yesu w…õn w…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôl ac…Ēl nŇč…õ aŇčwe ¬ę\it mir\it*¬Ľ m…Ē, mba Yesu …õnawos…õ f…õ wi k…ômun.  
\v 24 K…Ē as…Ēdar ŇčancaŇč Yesu d…ôt…Ēk y…õp…ômp…ôl, k…Ē Ňčayer…õn…õ yamos y…Ēn, Ňčakot…õ ti yampuŇčpuŇč ny…õ nw…õ o nw…õ eŇčkek…ôr…õ nde nd…Ēr…Ēn m…Ē.  
\v 25 Walaha w…õnayi nt…õ ŇčanccaŇč Yesu d…ôt…Ēk y…õp…ômp…ôl m…Ē.  
\v 26 Tecic…ôs nt…õ t…Ē Ňčanacic k…ôment…ôr ka tes nt…õ t…õnas…ĒŇč…õ k'andif k…Ē m…Ē: ¬ęW…ôb…õ ka aSuyif.¬Ľ  
\v 27 K…Ē ŇčancaŇč Yesu d…ôt…Ēk y…õp…ômp…ôl k…Ē calbante m…õr…ôŇč, w…ôkin p…ôyi k…Ē k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt, w…ôk…Ē p…ôyi k…Ē k…ôca k…ômeriya.  
\v 28 [\f + \fr 15:28 \ft Yecic…ôs yokur y…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē y…Ēl…Ēma y…Ēy…Ē f…õ moloku mam…õ: ¬ęTat…Ēk…Ē t…Ē tecic…ôs t…õnament…ôrn…õ, nt…õ t…õnaloku: ‚ÄĻK'anc…ômb…ôr k…Ē calbante dac…Ē.‚Äļ¬Ľ (M…ôm…Ēm…ôn s…Ē Luk 22.37 k…Ē Esayi 53.12.)\f*]  
\v 29 Acep…ôr Ňčacl…Ēm…ôs Mariki Yesu, Ňčacf…õk k…Ē domp. Ňäacloku: ¬ęM…ôna nw…õ m…ôncek…ôli k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu, m…ôc…ômb…ôr s…Ē ki mata maas disr…õ m…Ē,  
\v 30 m…ôyacn…õ m…ônas…ôrka, m…ôtor d…ôt…Ēk y…õp…ômp…ôl yay…õ!¬Ľ  
\v 31 AloŇčn…õ ap…ĒŇč k…Ē at…ôks…õ sariy…õ s'aSuyif, Ňča s…Ē Ňčancfani Yesu Ňčacloku: ¬ę∆źnayac al…Ēma, mba …Ēf…Ētam k…ôyacn…õ nk…Ēns…ôrka!  
\v 32 Krist, w…ôb…õ ka Yisrayel p…ôtor oŇč ma d…ôt…Ēk y…õp…ômp…ôl, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ s…ôn…ôŇčk s…ôlaŇč s…Ē ti m…Ē!¬Ľ Afum ak…Ē anacaŇč k…Ē Yesu m…Ē, Ňčancl…Ēm…ôs k…Ē s…Ē. 
\s1 Defi da Yesu 
\p  
\v 33 P…ôndeyi daŇč, dec dosur…õn…õ afum d…ôs…ôbomp, k…Ē kubump k…ôntor d…ônt…Ēf f…ôp, t…õnab…Ēl…õ k…ôt…õnc haŇč salifana.  
\v 34 Salifana s…ôndeb…ôp, k…Ē Yesu oŇčkul…õ-kul…õ: ¬ę\it Eloyi, Eloyi, lema sabaktani?\it*¬Ľ It…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē: ¬ęKanu kem, Kanu kem, ta ake t…Ē m…ôsak'em-…õ?¬Ľ\x - \xo 15:34 \xt Yabura 22.1\x* 
\v 35 Afum al…Ēma ak…Ē Ňčanayi di m…Ē Ňčanane k…Ē dim. Ňäancloku k…ôf…Ēt…Ē disr…õ: ¬ęM…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl, AŇčnabi Eli eyi k…ôwe tat…Ēk…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 36 K…Ē fum w…ôl…Ēma …õy…õks…õ, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôpuk yaŇčgba d…ôm…ônc…Ēnc…Ē, k'…õn…õps…ôr yi d…ôk…ômota, k'…Ēs…ĒŇč Yesu a p…ômun, p…ôcloku: ¬ęN…ôkar ma, pam…Ēm…ôn belbel k…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ a Eli endeder k…ôdetor…õ k…Ē-…õ.¬Ľ  
\v 37 Mba k…Ē Yesu owur…õ dim d…Ēp…ĒŇč, k'eŇčgbiŇč kifir.  
\v 38 K…Ē k…ôloto k…ôlel nk…õ k…ôŇčk…ôŇčk t…Ēks…Ē ta k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu m…Ē k…ôŇčgb…õr…õ dac…Ē, k…ôy…õf…õ tak…ôroŇč haŇč tant…Ēf.  
\v 39 Nt…õ an…ôŇčk Yesu k…ôgbiŇč k…Ēn kifir m…Ē, k…Ē w…ôb…õ k'as…Ēdar w…ôRom nw…õ …õnayi di p…ôt…õf…ôrn…õ k…Ē m…Ē, oloku: ¬ęFum w…ôkaw…õ, Wan ka Kanu yati …õnayi.¬Ľ  
\v 40 Aran s…Ē Ňčanac…ôm…õ p…ôb…Ēl…õ Ňčacm…Ēm…ôn. Aran akaŇč…õ dac…Ē: Mari w…ôka Makdala, Mari iya w…ôka Sak w…ôf…õt k…Ē Yoses, k…Ē w…ôran w…ôl…Ēma nw…õ ancwe Salome m…Ē.  
\v 41 Aran akak…Ē Ňčanac…ôm…õ Yesu dar…ôŇč, Ňčacb…ôc…õ k…Ē nt…õ …õnayi Kalile m…Ē, k…Ē aran alar…ôm al…Ēma aŇč…õ Ňčanap…õ k…Ē nk…Ēn Yesu Yerusal…õm m…Ē. 
\s1 Amb…õr Yesu d…ôkufu 
\p  
\v 42 D…Ēf…Ēy d…õmb…ôp, mba nt…õ p…ônay…Ēn…õ d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôlomp…ôsn…õn…õ simiti d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm m…Ē,  
\v 43 w…ôka Arimate w…ôl…Ēma nw…õ ancwe Isifu m…Ē …õmb…ôkn…õ, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē ndena Pilat k…ôk…Ētola k…Ē k…ôbel ka Yesu nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ p…ôwup ki m…Ē. Isifu, fum w…ôp…ĒŇč …õnayi aboc kiti aSuyif dac…Ē, nw…õ k…ôder ka d…õb…õ da Kanu k…ônabas m…Ē.  
\v 44 K…Ē p…ônciyan…õ Pilat k…ône a Yesu elip k…ôfi kat…ôna. K…Ē Pilat ewe w…ôb…õ w…ôs…Ēdar k'eyif k…Ē, k…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ a Yesu efina p…ôwon-…õ?  
\v 45 Nt…õ w…ôb…õ w…ôs…Ēdar oloku k…Ē t…Ēk…Ē t…õnayi m…Ē, k…Ē Pilat owos…õ Isifu k…ôl…õk k…ôbel ka Yesu.  
\v 46 K…Ē Isifu …õway ar…Ēf…ôn Ňča k…ôloto k…ôtel…ôr, k'ontor…õ Yesu d…ôt…Ēk y…õp…ômp…ôl, k'…õn…õps…ôr k…Ē Ňči, k'omboc k…Ē d…ôkufu nk…õ anay…Ēk d…ôtasar m…Ē. Nt…õ elip m…Ē, k'embiŇčk…ôli tasar mp…õ …õnasunc…õ d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ da kufu kaŇčk…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 47 Mari w…ôka Makdala k…Ē Mari, iya ka Yoses, Ňčacgb…õk…ôr…õ nde k…ôfo nk…õ anab…õr k…Ē m…Ē. 
\c 16  
\s1 Yesu k…ôf…Ēt…õ k…Ēn afi dac…Ē 
\p  
\v 1 Nt…õ simiti d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm dencep…ôr m…Ē, d…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk sandeŇč, k…Ē Mari w…ôka dare da Makdala, Mari iya ka Sak, k…Ē w…ôran w…ôl…Ēma Salome Ňčaway moro mobotu amb…Ēnc, k…ôdesop mi k…ôbel ka Yesu.  
\v 2 Tataka ta sandeŇč b…ôtb…ôt suy, k…Ē Ňčander nde d…ôkufu.  
\v 3 Ňäacyift…õn…õ taŇčan: ¬ęAn'…ĒŇčk…ĒbiŇčk…ôl…õ su tasar t…Ēk…Ē asunc…õ d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ da kufu m…Ē-…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 4 Ňäandeyekti f…Ēr, k…Ē Ňčan…ôŇčk tasar p…Ēp…ĒŇč pap…Ēk…Ē pabiŇčk…ôli pi.  
\v 5 Nt…õ Ňčancb…õr…õ d…ôkufu m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčan…ôŇčk w…ôt…õmp w…ôl…Ēma p…ônd…õ k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt, p…ôb…õrn…õ duma dobolu defer, k…Ē Ňčanes…õ.  
\v 6 K…Ē w…ôt…õmp nw…õ oloku Ňča: ¬ęTa n…ônes…õ. Yesu w…ôka Nasar…õt n…ônt…õn, w…ôk…Ē anacaŇč d…ôt…Ēk y…õp…ômp…ôl m…Ē. ∆Üf…Ēt…õ afi dac…Ē, eyi f…õ nn…Ē! N…ôn…ôŇčk k…ôfo nk…õ k'anaboc k…Ē.  
\v 7 Mba n…ôk…Ē n…ôloku ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč k…Ē Piy…õr a Yesu eyi nu kiriŇč k…ôk…Ē Kalile: Dif…Ē n…ôŇčk…Ēn…ôŇčk k…Ē, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē …õnaloku nu ti m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 8 K…Ē aran aŇč…õ Ňčawur d…ôndo d…ôkufu k…Ē Ňčay…õks…õ, Ňčacyikc…õ, cusu c…ôwos Ňča. Ali tes Ňčanaloku f…õ fum, bawo Ňčananes…õ. 
\s1 Yesu ement…ôrn…õ Mari w…ôka Makdala 
\p  
\v 9 [Nt…õ Yesu …Ēf…Ēt…õ defi m…Ē, b…ôtb…ôt ba tataka t…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē ta tataka toluks…ôr, k'owur…ôr k…ôr…õsna Mari w…ôka Makdala, w…ôk…Ē Yesu …õnab…õl…ôs y…ĒŇčk y…õl…õc cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč m…Ē.  
\v 10 K…Ē Mari w…ôka Makdala …ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôloku moloku mam…Ēk…Ē ak…Ē Ňčanak…Ē k…Ē nk…Ēn, Ňčayi k…ôbal ka defi da Yesu, Ňčacbok m…Ē.  
\v 11 Nt…õ afum akaŇč…õ Ňčanane a eyi w…ôyeŇč, a nk…Ēn Mari w…ôka Makdala …õnan…ôŇčk k…Ē m…Ē, ŇčanalaŇč f…õ ti. 
\s1 Yesu ement…ôrn…õ ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč 
\p  
\v 12 Nt…õ tat…Ēk…Ē tencep…ôr m…Ē, k…Ē Yesu ement…ôrn…õ s…Ē teyi t…Ēl…Ēma ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč m…õr…ôŇč aŇč…õ Ňčanck…Ē d…ôkulum m…Ē.  
\v 13 K…Ē akak…Ē m…õr…ôŇč Ňčander s…Ē Ňčaloku ti ac…õps…õ a Yesu dar…ôŇč alp…ôs ak…Ē. Ňäa s…Ē, ŇčanalaŇč f…õ Ňča. 
\s1 Yesu ement…ôrn…õ ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč aŇč…õ w…ôco k…Ē pin 
\p  
\v 14 T…õlp…ôs oŇč, k…Ē Yesu ement…ôrn…õ ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč aŇč…õ w…ôco k…Ē pin, t…õm nt…õ Ňčacdi yeri m…Ē, k'…õnal Ňča k…ôbut k…ôŇčan k…ôlaŇč k…Ē k…ôyeŇčk domp k…ôŇčan, bawo ŇčanalaŇč f…õ ak…Ē Ňčanan…ôŇčk k…Ē nt…õ …õnaf…Ēt…õ afi dac…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 15 K…Ē Yesu oloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ôk…Ē doru dand…õ f…ôp, n…ôk…Ē n…ôcam Kibaru K…ôt…Ēt nn…Ē afum a doru f…ôp Ňčayi m…Ē.  
\v 16 M…ôna nw…õ m…ôŇčy…Ēn…õ w…ôlaŇč, m…ôs…Ēt…Ē k…ôgb…ôt d…ôromun teta Kanu m…Ē, aŇčyac …ôm, mba m…ôna nw…õ m…ônt…ĒlaŇč m…Ē, ant…Ēr…ôs …ôm d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôkiti.  
\v 17 N…ôn…ôŇčk m…õgb…õk…ôr…õ mm…õ mendesol…õ aŇč…õ Ňčandey…Ēn…õ alaŇč m…Ē: Tewe tem tendes…ĒŇč…õ Ňčacb…õl…ôs y…ĒŇčk y…õl…õc. Ňäande Ňčacc…Ēp cusu nc…õ Ňčanat…Ēc…ôr…õ m…Ē.  
\v 18 Ňäande Ňčacsump…ôr…õ bok waca. Pomun p…õk…ônt…ôŇč mp…õ o mp…õ p…Ē Ňčamun p…Ēf…Ēy…Ē Ňča t…Ēl…Ēm o t…Ēl…Ēm. Ňäande ŇčacdeŇč acuy waca, akak…Ē Ňčactamn…õ.¬Ľ 
\s1 Yesu olukus Kanu k…ôs…ôk 
\p  
\v 19 Mariki Yesu, nt…õ elip k…ôlok-lok…ôr Ňča m…Ē, k'amp…õn…õ k…Ē d…ôK…Ēm, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ônd…õ Kanu k…ôs…ôk.]\f + \fr 16:19 \ft Yecic…ôs yecep…ôr yokur m…õr…ôŇč, k…Ē y…Ēl…Ēma ny…õ alaŇč m…Ē, y…Ēy…Ē f…õ moloku m…õlp…ôs ma kibaru kaŇčk…õ k…ôy…õf…õ sora 9 haŇč 19. Moloku mam…õ d…ôyecic…ôs yofu y…õlp…ôs meyi.\f* 
\v 20 K…Ē ac…õps…õ a Yesu dar…ôŇč ŇčaŇčk…Ē mofo f…ôp k…ôk…Ēsams…ôr Kibaru K…ôt…Ēt. Mariki …õncb…ôc k…Ē Ňča, p…ôcs…ĒŇč…õ d…ôm…õgb…õk…ôr…õ mm…õ Ňčancwur…õ, paclaŇč moloku mam…Ēk…Ē.\f + \fr 16:20 \ft Moloku mm…õ meyi f…õ Yecic…ôs Yosoku yokur f…ôp: ¬ęMba p…ôpic p…Ē Ňčancloku asol a Piy…õr nt…õ anasom Ňča k…ôloku m…Ē. Nt…õ tencep…ôr m…Ē, Yesu nk…Ēns…ôrka osom Ňča k…ôkek…ôr…õ kawandi k…ôpus nk…õ k…ônt…Ēlip m…Ē k…ôy…õf…õ nde dec d…õmp…õ k…ôk…Ē ka nde d…õŇčkal…õ m…Ē, k…ôyac ka doru o doru nk…õ k…ônt…Ēlip m…Ē. Amina¬Ľ \f*